159 // Work around for a NVCC compiler bug which causes it to fail
160 // to compile std::ratio_{multiply,divide} when used directly
161 // in the std::chrono::duration template instantiations below
162 namespace detail {
163 template <typename R1, typename R2>
164 using ratio_multiply = decltype(std::ratio_multiply<R1, R2>{});
165 
166 template <typename R1, typename R2>
167 using ratio_divide = decltype(std::ratio_divide<R1, R2>{});
168 } // namespace detail
169

171 // Interface |

173 
174 // durations
175 
176 using days = std::chrono::duration
177  <int, detail::ratio_multiply<std::ratio<24>, std::chrono::hours::period>>;
178 
179 using weeks = std::chrono::duration
180  <int, detail::ratio_multiply<std::ratio<7>, days::period>>;
181 
182 using years = std::chrono::duration
183  <int, detail::ratio_multiply<std::ratio<146097, 400>, days::period>>;
184 
185 using months = std::chrono::duration
186  <int, detail::ratio_divide<years::period, std::ratio<12>>>;
187 
188 // time_point
189 
190 template <class Duration>
191  using sys_time = std::chrono::time_point<std::chrono::system_clock, Duration>;
192 
193 using sys_days = sys_time<days>;
194 using sys_seconds = sys_time<std::chrono::seconds>;
195 
196 struct local_t {};
197 
198 template <class Duration>
199  using local_time = std::chrono::time_point<local_t, Duration>;
200 
201 using local_seconds = local_time<std::chrono::seconds>;
202 using local_days = local_time<days>;

1016 template<class CharT, class Traits = std::char_traits<CharT>>
1017 class save_istream
1018 {
1019 protected:
1020  std::basic_ios<CharT, Traits>& is_;
1021  CharT fill_;
1022  std::ios::fmtflags flags_;
1023  std::streamsize width_;
1024  std::basic_ostream<CharT, Traits>* tie_;
1025  std::locale loc_;
1026 
1027 public:
1028  ~save_istream()
1029  {
1030  is_.fill(fill_);
1031  is_.flags(flags_);
1032  is_.width(width_);
1033  is_.imbue(loc_);
1034  is_.tie(tie_);
1035  }
1036 
1037  save_istream(const save_istream&) = delete;
1038  save_istream& operator=(const save_istream&) = delete;
1039 
1040  explicit save_istream(std::basic_ios<CharT, Traits>& is)
1041  : is_(is)
1042  , fill_(is.fill())
1043  , flags_(is.flags())
1044  , width_(is.width(0))
1045  , tie_(is.tie(nullptr))
1046  , loc_(is.getloc())
1047  {
1048  if (tie_ != nullptr)
1049  tie_->flush();
1050  }
1051 };
1052 
1053 template<class CharT, class Traits = std::char_traits<CharT>>
1054 class save_ostream
1055  : private save_istream<CharT, Traits>
1056 {
1057 public:
1058  ~save_ostream()
1059  {
1060  if ((this->flags_ & std::ios::unitbuf) &&
1061 #if HAS_UNCAUGHT_EXCEPTIONS
1062  std::uncaught_exceptions() == 0 &&
1063 #else
1064  !std::uncaught_exception() &&
1065 #endif
1066  this->is_.good())
1067  this->is_.rdbuf()->pubsync();
1068  }
1069 
1070  save_ostream(const save_ostream&) = delete;
1071  save_ostream& operator=(const save_ostream&) = delete;
1072 
1073  explicit save_ostream(std::basic_ios<CharT, Traits>& os)
1074  : save_istream<CharT, Traits>(os)
1075  {
1076  }
1077 };
1078 
1079 template <class T>
1080 struct choose_trunc_type
1081 {
1082  static const int digits = std::numeric_limits<T>::digits;
1083  using type = typename std::conditional
1084  <
1085  digits < 32,
1086  std::int32_t,
1087  typename std::conditional
1088  <
1089  digits < 64,
1090  std::int64_t,
1091 #ifdef __SIZEOF_INT128__
1092  __int128
1093 #else
1094  std::int64_t
1095 #endif
1096  >::type
1097  >::type;
1098 };
1099 
1100 template <class T>
1101 CONSTCD11
1102 inline
1103 typename std::enable_if
1104 <
1105  !std::chrono::treat_as_floating_point<T>::value,
1106  T
1107 >::type
1108 trunc(T t) NOEXCEPT
1109 {
1110  return t;
1111 }
1112 
1113 template <class T>
1114 CONSTCD14
1115 inline
1116 typename std::enable_if
1117 <
1118  std::chrono::treat_as_floating_point<T>::value,
1119  T
1120 >::type
1121 trunc(T t) NOEXCEPT
1122 {
1123  using std::numeric_limits;
1124  using I = typename choose_trunc_type<T>::type;
1125  CONSTDATA auto digits = numeric_limits<T>::digits;
1126  static_assert(digits < numeric_limits<I>::digits, "");
1127  CONSTDATA auto max = I{1} << (digits-1);
1128  CONSTDATA auto min = -max;
1129  const auto negative = t < T{0};
1130  if (min <= t && t <= max && t != 0 && t == t)
1131  {
1132  t = static_cast<T>(static_cast<I>(t));
1133  if (t == 0 && negative)
1134  t = -t;
1135  }
1136  return t;
1137 }
1138 
1139 template <std::intmax_t Xp, std::intmax_t Yp>
1140 struct static_gcd
1141 {
1142  static const std::intmax_t value = static_gcd<Yp, Xp % Yp>::value;
1143 };
1144 
1145 template <std::intmax_t Xp>
1146 struct static_gcd<Xp, 0>
1147 {
1148  static const std::intmax_t value = Xp;
1149 };
1150 
1151 template <>
1152 struct static_gcd<0, 0>
1153 {
1154  static const std::intmax_t value = 1;
1155 };
1156 
1157 template <class R1, class R2>
1158 struct no_overflow
1159 {
1160 private:
1161  static const std::intmax_t gcd_n1_n2 = static_gcd<R1::num, R2::num>::value;
1162  static const std::intmax_t gcd_d1_d2 = static_gcd<R1::den, R2::den>::value;
1163  static const std::intmax_t n1 = R1::num / gcd_n1_n2;
1164  static const std::intmax_t d1 = R1::den / gcd_d1_d2;
1165  static const std::intmax_t n2 = R2::num / gcd_n1_n2;
1166  static const std::intmax_t d2 = R2::den / gcd_d1_d2;
1167 #ifdef __cpp_constexpr
1168  static const std::intmax_t max = std::numeric_limits<std::intmax_t>::max();
1169 #else
1170  static const std::intmax_t max = LLONG_MAX;
1171 #endif
1172 
1173  template <std::intmax_t Xp, std::intmax_t Yp, bool overflow>
1174  struct mul // overflow == false
1175  {
1176  static const std::intmax_t value = Xp * Yp;
1177  };
1178 
1179  template <std::intmax_t Xp, std::intmax_t Yp>
1180  struct mul<Xp, Yp, true>
1181  {
1182  static const std::intmax_t value = 1;
1183  };
1184 
1185 public:
1186  static const bool value = (n1 <= max / d2) && (n2 <= max / d1);
1187  typedef std::ratio<mul<n1, d2, !value>::value,
1188  mul<n2, d1, !value>::value> type;
1189 };
1190 
1191 } // detail
1192 
1193 // trunc towards zero
1194 template <class To, class Rep, class Period>
1195 CONSTCD11
1196 inline
1197 typename std::enable_if
1198 <
1199  detail::no_overflow<Period, typename To::period>::value,
1200  To
1201 >::type
1202 trunc(const std::chrono::duration<Rep, Period>& d)
1203 {
1204  return To{detail::trunc(std::chrono::duration_cast<To>(d).count())};
1205 }
1206 
1207 template <class To, class Rep, class Period>
1208 CONSTCD11
1209 inline
1210 typename std::enable_if
1211 <
1212  !detail::no_overflow<Period, typename To::period>::value,
1213  To
1214 >::type
1215 trunc(const std::chrono::duration<Rep, Period>& d)
1216 {
1217  using std::chrono::duration_cast;
1218  using std::chrono::duration;
1219  using rep = typename std::common_type<Rep, typename To::rep>::type;
1220  return To{detail::trunc(duration_cast<To>(duration_cast<duration<rep>>(d)).count())};
1221 }
1222 
1223 #ifndef HAS_CHRONO_ROUNDING
1224 # if defined(_MSC_FULL_VER) && (_MSC_FULL_VER >= 190023918 || (_MSC_FULL_VER >= 190000000 && defined (__clang__)))
1225 # define HAS_CHRONO_ROUNDING 1
1226 # elif defined(__cpp_lib_chrono) && __cplusplus > 201402 && __cpp_lib_chrono >= 201510
1227 # define HAS_CHRONO_ROUNDING 1
1228 # elif defined(_LIBCPP_VERSION) && __cplusplus > 201402 && _LIBCPP_VERSION >= 3800
1229 # define HAS_CHRONO_ROUNDING 1
1230 # else
1231 # define HAS_CHRONO_ROUNDING 0
1232 # endif
1233 #endif // HAS_CHRONO_ROUNDING
1234 
1235 #if HAS_CHRONO_ROUNDING == 0
1236 
1237 // round down
1238 template <class To, class Rep, class Period>
1239 CONSTCD14
1240 inline
1241 typename std::enable_if
1242 <
1243  detail::no_overflow<Period, typename To::period>::value,
1244  To
1245 >::type
1246 floor(const std::chrono::duration<Rep, Period>& d)
1247 {
1248  auto t = trunc<To>(d);
1249  if (t > d)
1250  return t - To{1};
1251  return t;
1252 }
1253 
1254 template <class To, class Rep, class Period>
1255 CONSTCD14
1256 inline
1257 typename std::enable_if
1258 <
1259  !detail::no_overflow<Period, typename To::period>::value,
1260  To
1261 >::type
1262 floor(const std::chrono::duration<Rep, Period>& d)
1263 {
1264  using rep = typename std::common_type<Rep, typename To::rep>::type;
1265  return floor<To>(floor<std::chrono::duration<rep>>(d));
1266 }
1267 
1268 // round to nearest, to even on tie
1269 template <class To, class Rep, class Period>
1270 CONSTCD14
1271 inline
1272 To
1273 round(const std::chrono::duration<Rep, Period>& d)
1274 {
1275  auto t0 = floor<To>(d);
1276  auto t1 = t0 + To{1};
1277  if (t1 == To{0} && t0 < To{0})
1278  t1 = -t1;
1279  auto diff0 = d - t0;
1280  auto diff1 = t1 - d;
1281  if (diff0 == diff1)
1282  {
1283  if (t0 - trunc<To>(t0/2)*2 == To{0})
1284  return t0;
1285  return t1;
1286  }
1287  if (diff0 < diff1)
1288  return t0;
1289  return t1;
1290 }
1291 
1292 // round up
1293 template <class To, class Rep, class Period>
1294 CONSTCD14
1295 inline
1296 To
1297 ceil(const std::chrono::duration<Rep, Period>& d)
1298 {
1299  auto t = trunc<To>(d);
1300  if (t < d)
1301  return t + To{1};
1302  return t;
1303 }
1304 
1305 template <class Rep, class Period,
1306  class = typename std::enable_if
1307  <
1308  std::numeric_limits<Rep>::is_signed
1309  >::type>
1310 CONSTCD11
1311 std::chrono::duration<Rep, Period>
1312 abs(std::chrono::duration<Rep, Period> d)
1313 {
1314  return d >= d.zero() ? d : -d;
1315 }

2187 template<class>
2188 CONSTCD14
2189 inline
2190 year_month
2191 operator+(const year_month& ym, const months& dm) NOEXCEPT
2192 {
2193  auto dmi = static_cast<int>(static_cast<unsigned>(ym.month())) - 1 + dm.count();
2194  auto dy = (dmi >= 0 ? dmi : dmi-11) / 12;
2195  dmi = dmi - dy * 12 + 1;
2196  return (ym.year() + years(dy)) / month(static_cast<unsigned>(dmi));
2197 }
2198

2222  return (x.year() - y.year()) +

2270 CONSTCD14
2271 inline
2272 bool
2273 month_day::ok() const NOEXCEPT
2274 {
2275  CONSTDATA date::day d[] =
2276  {
2277  date::day(31), date::day(29), date::day(31),
2278  date::day(30), date::day(31), date::day(30),
2279  date::day(31), date::day(31), date::day(30),
2280  date::day(31), date::day(30), date::day(31)
2281  };
2282  return m_.ok() && date::day{1} <= d_ && d_ <= d[static_cast<unsigned>(m_)-1];
2283 }

2788 CONSTCD14
2789 inline
2790 days
2791 year_month_day::to_days() const NOEXCEPT
2792 {
2793  static_assert(std::numeric_limits<unsigned>::digits >= 18,
2794  "This algorithm has not been ported to a 16 bit unsigned integer");
2795  static_assert(std::numeric_limits<int>::digits >= 20,
2796  "This algorithm has not been ported to a 16 bit signed integer");
2797  auto const y = static_cast<int>(y_) - (m_ <= February);
2798  auto const m = static_cast<unsigned>(m_);
2799  auto const d = static_cast<unsigned>(d_);
2800  auto const era = (y >= 0 ? y : y-399) / 400;
2801  auto const yoe = static_cast<unsigned>(y - era * 400); // [0, 399]
2802  auto const doy = (153*(m > 2 ? m-3 : m+9) + 2)/5 + d-1; // [0, 365]
2803  auto const doe = yoe * 365 + yoe/4 - yoe/100 + doy; // [0, 146096]
2804  return days{era * 146097 + static_cast<int>(doe) - 719468};
2805 }
2806 
2807 CONSTCD14
2808 inline
2809 year_month_day::operator sys_days() const NOEXCEPT
2810 {
2811  return sys_days{to_days()};
2812 }
2813 
2814 CONSTCD14
2815 inline
2816 year_month_day::operator local_days() const NOEXCEPT
2817 {
2818  return local_days{to_days()};
2819 }
2820 
2821 CONSTCD14
2822 inline
2823 bool
2824 year_month_day::ok() const NOEXCEPT
2825 {
2826  if (!(y_.ok() && m_.ok()))
2827  return false;
2828  return date::day{1} <= d_ && d_ <= (y_ / m_ / last).day();
2829 }

2853  : (x.year() > y.year() ? false
2854  : (x.month() < y.month() ? true
2855  : (x.month() > y.month() ? false
2856  : (x.day() < y.day()))));
2857 }

2883 template<class CharT, class Traits>
2884 inline
2885 std::basic_ostream<CharT, Traits>&
2886 operator<<(std::basic_ostream<CharT, Traits>& os, const year_month_day& ymd)
2887 {
2888  detail::save_ostream<CharT, Traits> _(os);
2889  os.fill('0');
2890  os.flags(std::ios::dec | std::ios::right);
2891  os.imbue(std::locale::classic());
2892  os << ymd.year() << '-';
2893  os.width(2);
2894  os << static_cast<unsigned>(ymd.month()) << '-';
2895  os << ymd.day();
2896  if (!ymd.ok())
2897  os << " is not a valid date";
2898  return os;
2899 }
2900 
2901 CONSTCD14
2902 inline
2903 year_month_day
2904 year_month_day::from_days(days dp) NOEXCEPT
2905 {
2906  static_assert(std::numeric_limits<unsigned>::digits >= 18,
2907  "This algorithm has not been ported to a 16 bit unsigned integer");
2908  static_assert(std::numeric_limits<int>::digits >= 20,
2909  "This algorithm has not been ported to a 16 bit signed integer");
2910  auto const z = dp.count() + 719468;
2911  auto const era = (z >= 0 ? z : z - 146096) / 146097;
2912  auto const doe = static_cast<unsigned>(z - era * 146097); // [0, 146096]
2913  auto const yoe = (doe - doe/1460 + doe/36524 - doe/146096) / 365; // [0, 399]
2914  auto const y = static_cast<days::rep>(yoe) + era * 400;
2915  auto const doy = doe - (365*yoe + yoe/4 - yoe/100); // [0, 365]
2916  auto const mp = (5*doy + 2)/153; // [0, 11]
2917  auto const d = doy - (153*mp+2)/5 + 1; // [1, 31]
2918  auto const m = mp < 10 ? mp+3 : mp-9; // [1, 12]
2919  return year_month_day{date::year{y + (m <= 2)}, date::month(m), date::day(d)};
2920 }

2927 {

2929 }

3076 CONSTCD14
3077 inline
3078 bool
3079 year_month_weekday::ok() const NOEXCEPT
3080 {
3081  if (!y_.ok() || !m_.ok() || !wdi_.weekday().ok() || wdi_.index() < 1)
3082  return false;
3083  if (wdi_.index() <= 4)
3084  return true;
3085  auto d2 = wdi_.weekday() - date::weekday(static_cast<sys_days>(y_/m_/1)) +
3086  days((wdi_.index()-1)*7 + 1);
3087  return static_cast<unsigned>(d2.count()) <= static_cast<unsigned>((y_/m_/last).day());
3088 }
3089 
3090 CONSTCD14
3091 inline
3092 year_month_weekday
3093 year_month_weekday::from_days(days d) NOEXCEPT
3094 {
3095  sys_days dp{d};
3096  auto const wd = date::weekday(dp);
3097  auto const ymd = year_month_day(dp);
3098  return {ymd.year(), ymd.month(), wd[(static_cast<unsigned>(ymd.day())-1)/7+1]};
3099 }
3100 
3101 CONSTCD14
3102 inline
3103 days
3104 year_month_weekday::to_days() const NOEXCEPT
3105 {
3106  auto d = sys_days(y_/m_/1);
3107  return (d + (wdi_.weekday() - date::weekday(d) + days{(wdi_.index()-1)*7})
3108  ).time_since_epoch();
3109 }

3716 struct undocumented {explicit undocumented() = default;};
3717 
3718 // width<n>::value is the number of fractional decimal digits in 1/n
3719 // width<0>::value and width<1>::value are defined to be 0
3720 // If 1/n takes more than 18 fractional decimal digits,
3721 // the result is truncated to 19.
3722 // Example: width<2>::value == 1
3723 // Example: width<3>::value == 19
3724 // Example: width<4>::value == 2
3725 // Example: width<10>::value == 1
3726 // Example: width<1000>::value == 3
3727 template <std::uint64_t n, std::uint64_t d, unsigned w = 0,
3728  bool should_continue = n%d != 0 && (w < 19)>
3729 struct width
3730 {
3731  static_assert(d > 0, "width called with zero denominator");
3732  static CONSTDATA unsigned value = 1 + width<n%d*10, d, w+1>::value;
3733 };
3734 
3735 template <std::uint64_t n, std::uint64_t d, unsigned w>
3736 struct width<n, d, w, false>
3737 {
3738  static CONSTDATA unsigned value = 0;
3739 };
3740 
3741 template <unsigned exp>
3742 struct static_pow10
3743 {
3744 private:
3745  static CONSTDATA std::uint64_t h = static_pow10<exp/2>::value;
3746 public:
3747  static CONSTDATA std::uint64_t value = h * h * (exp % 2 ? 10 : 1);
3748 };
3749 
3750 template <>
3751 struct static_pow10<0>
3752 {
3753  static CONSTDATA std::uint64_t value = 1;
3754 };
3755 
3756 template <class Duration>
3757 class decimal_format_seconds
3758 {
3759  using CT = typename std::common_type<Duration, std::chrono::seconds>::type;
3760  using rep = typename CT::rep;
3761  static unsigned CONSTDATA trial_width =
3762  detail::width<CT::period::num, CT::period::den>::value;
3763 public:
3764  static unsigned CONSTDATA width = trial_width < 19 ? trial_width : 6u;
3765  using precision = std::chrono::duration<rep,
3766  std::ratio<1, static_pow10<width>::value>>;
3767 
3768 private:
3769  std::chrono::seconds s_;
3770  precision sub_s_;
3771 
3772 public:
3773  CONSTCD11 decimal_format_seconds()
3774  : s_()
3775  , sub_s_()
3776  {}
3777 
3778  CONSTCD11 explicit decimal_format_seconds(const Duration& d) NOEXCEPT
3779  : s_(std::chrono::duration_cast<std::chrono::seconds>(d))
3780  , sub_s_(std::chrono::duration_cast<precision>(d - s_))
3781  {}
3782 
3783  CONSTCD14 std::chrono::seconds& seconds() NOEXCEPT {return s_;}
3784  CONSTCD11 std::chrono::seconds seconds() const NOEXCEPT {return s_;}
3785  CONSTCD11 precision subseconds() const NOEXCEPT {return sub_s_;}
3786 
3787  CONSTCD14 precision to_duration() const NOEXCEPT
3788  {
3789  return s_ + sub_s_;
3790  }
3791 
3792  CONSTCD11 bool in_conventional_range() const NOEXCEPT
3793  {
3794  return sub_s_ < std::chrono::seconds{1} && s_ < std::chrono::minutes{1};
3795  }
3796 
3797  template <class CharT, class Traits>
3798  friend
3799  std::basic_ostream<CharT, Traits>&
3800  operator<<(std::basic_ostream<CharT, Traits>& os, const decimal_format_seconds& x)
3801  {
3802  return x.print(os, std::chrono::treat_as_floating_point<rep>{});
3803  }
3804 
3805  template <class CharT, class Traits>
3806  std::basic_ostream<CharT, Traits>&
3807  print(std::basic_ostream<CharT, Traits>& os, std::true_type) const
3808  {
3809  date::detail::save_ostream<CharT, Traits> _(os);
3810  std::chrono::duration<rep> d = s_ + sub_s_;
3811  if (d < std::chrono::seconds{10})
3812  os << '0';
3813  os << std::fixed << d.count();
3814  return os;
3815  }
3816 
3817  template <class CharT, class Traits>
3818  std::basic_ostream<CharT, Traits>&
3819  print(std::basic_ostream<CharT, Traits>& os, std::false_type) const
3820  {
3821  date::detail::save_ostream<CharT, Traits> _(os);
3822  os.fill('0');
3823  os.flags(std::ios::dec | std::ios::right);
3824  os.width(2);
3825  os << s_.count();
3826  if (width > 0)
3827  {
3828 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
3829  os << std::use_facet<std::numpunct<CharT>>(os.getloc()).decimal_point();
3830 #else
3831  os << '.';
3832 #endif
3833  date::detail::save_ostream<CharT, Traits> _s(os);
3834  os.imbue(std::locale::classic());
3835  os.width(width);
3836  os << sub_s_.count();
3837  }
3838  return os;
3839  }
3840 };

3844 CONSTCD11
3845 typename std::enable_if
3846  <

3848  std::chrono::duration<Rep, Period>

3870 template <class Duration>
3871 class hh_mm_ss
3872 {
3873  using dfs = detail::decimal_format_seconds<typename std::common_type<Duration,
3874  std::chrono::seconds>::type>;
3875 
3876  std::chrono::hours h_;
3877  std::chrono::minutes m_;
3878  dfs s_;
3879  bool neg_;
3880 
3881 public:
3882  static unsigned CONSTDATA fractional_width = dfs::width;
3883  using precision = typename dfs::precision;
3884 
3885  CONSTCD11 hh_mm_ss() NOEXCEPT
3886  : hh_mm_ss(Duration::zero())
3887  {}
3888 
3889  CONSTCD11 explicit hh_mm_ss(Duration d) NOEXCEPT
3890  : h_(std::chrono::duration_cast<std::chrono::hours>(detail::abs(d)))
3891  , m_(std::chrono::duration_cast<std::chrono::minutes>(detail::abs(d)) - h_)
3892  , s_(detail::abs(d) - h_ - m_)
3893  , neg_(d < Duration::zero())
3894  {}
3895 
3896  CONSTCD11 std::chrono::hours hours() const NOEXCEPT {return h_;}
3897  CONSTCD11 std::chrono::minutes minutes() const NOEXCEPT {return m_;}
3898  CONSTCD11 std::chrono::seconds seconds() const NOEXCEPT {return s_.seconds();}
3899  CONSTCD14 std::chrono::seconds&
3900  seconds(detail::undocumented) NOEXCEPT {return s_.seconds();}
3901  CONSTCD11 precision subseconds() const NOEXCEPT {return s_.subseconds();}
3902  CONSTCD11 bool is_negative() const NOEXCEPT {return neg_;}
3903 
3904  CONSTCD11 explicit operator precision() const NOEXCEPT {return to_duration();}
3905  CONSTCD11 precision to_duration() const NOEXCEPT
3906  {return (s_.to_duration() + m_ + h_) * (1-2*neg_);}
3907 
3908  CONSTCD11 bool in_conventional_range() const NOEXCEPT
3909  {
3910  return !neg_ && h_ < days{1} && m_ < std::chrono::hours{1} &&
3911  s_.in_conventional_range();
3912  }
3913 
3914 private:
3915 
3916  template <class charT, class traits>
3917  friend
3918  std::basic_ostream<charT, traits>&
3919  operator<<(std::basic_ostream<charT, traits>& os, hh_mm_ss const& tod)
3920  {
3921  if (tod.is_negative())
3922  os << '-';
3923  if (tod.h_ < std::chrono::hours{10})
3924  os << '0';
3925  os << tod.h_.count() << ':';
3926  if (tod.m_ < std::chrono::minutes{10})
3927  os << '0';
3928  os << tod.m_.count() << ':' << tod.s_;
3929  return os;
3930  }

3957 CONSTCD14
3958 bool
3959 is_pm(std::chrono::hours const& h) NOEXCEPT
3960 {

3962  return hours{12} <= h && h < hours{24};
3963 }
3964 
3965 inline
3966 CONSTCD14
3967 std::chrono::hours
3968 make12(std::chrono::hours h) NOEXCEPT
3969 {
3970  using std::chrono::hours;
3971  if (h < hours{12})
3972  {
3973  if (h == hours{0})
3974  h = hours{12};
3975  }
3976  else
3977  {
3978  if (h != hours{12})
3979  h = h - hours{12};
3980  }
3981  return h;
3982 }
3983 
3984 inline
3985 CONSTCD14
3986 std::chrono::hours
3987 make24(std::chrono::hours h, bool is_pm) NOEXCEPT
3988 {
3989  using std::chrono::hours;
3990  if (is_pm)
3991  {
3992  if (h != hours{12})
3993  h = h + hours{12};
3994  }
3995  else if (h == hours{12})
3996  h = hours{0};
3997  return h;
3998 }

4163 template <class CharT1, class CharT2, std::size_t N1, std::size_t N2>
4164 CONSTCD14
4165 inline
4166 string_literal<typename std::conditional<sizeof(CharT2) <= sizeof(CharT1), CharT1, CharT2>::type,
4167  N1 + N2 - 1>
4168 operator+(const string_literal<CharT1, N1>& x, const string_literal<CharT2, N2>& y) NOEXCEPT
4169 {
4170  using CT = typename std::conditional<sizeof(CharT2) <= sizeof(CharT1), CharT1, CharT2>::type;
4171 
4172  string_literal<CT, N1 + N2 - 1> r;
4173  std::size_t i = 0;
4174  for (; i < N1-1; ++i)
4175  r.p_[i] = CT(x.p_[i]);
4176  for (std::size_t j = 0; j < N2; ++j, ++i)
4177  r.p_[i] = CT(y.p_[j]);
4178 
4179  return r;
4180 }

4592 template <class Duration>
4593 struct fields
4594 {
4595  year_month_day ymd{nanyear/0/0};
4596  weekday wd{8u};
4597  hh_mm_ss<Duration> tod{};
4598  bool has_tod = false;
4599 
4600  fields() = default;
4601 
4602  fields(year_month_day ymd_) : ymd(ymd_) {}
4603  fields(weekday wd_) : wd(wd_) {}
4604  fields(hh_mm_ss<Duration> tod_) : tod(tod_), has_tod(true) {}
4605 
4606  fields(year_month_day ymd_, weekday wd_) : ymd(ymd_), wd(wd_) {}
4607  fields(year_month_day ymd_, hh_mm_ss<Duration> tod_) : ymd(ymd_), tod(tod_),
4608  has_tod(true) {}
4609 
4610  fields(weekday wd_, hh_mm_ss<Duration> tod_) : wd(wd_), tod(tod_), has_tod(true) {}
4611 
4612  fields(year_month_day ymd_, weekday wd_, hh_mm_ss<Duration> tod_)
4613  : ymd(ymd_)
4614  , wd(wd_)
4615  , tod(tod_)
4616  , has_tod(true)
4617  {}
4618 };

4623 template <class CharT, class Traits, class Duration>
4624 unsigned
4625 extract_weekday(std::basic_ostream<CharT, Traits>& os, const fields<Duration>& fds)
4626 {
4627  if (!fds.ymd.ok() && !fds.wd.ok())
4628  {
4629  // fds does not contain a valid weekday
4630  os.setstate(std::ios::failbit);
4631  return 8;
4632  }
4633  weekday wd;
4634  if (fds.ymd.ok())
4635  {
4636  wd = weekday{sys_days(fds.ymd)};
4637  if (fds.wd.ok() && wd != fds.wd)
4638  {
4639  // fds.ymd and fds.wd are inconsistent
4640  os.setstate(std::ios::failbit);
4641  return 8;
4642  }
4643  }
4644  else
4645  wd = fds.wd;
4646  return static_cast<unsigned>((wd - Sunday).count());
4647 }
4648 
4649 template <class CharT, class Traits, class Duration>
4650 unsigned
4651 extract_month(std::basic_ostream<CharT, Traits>& os, const fields<Duration>& fds)
4652 {
4653  if (!fds.ymd.month().ok())
4654  {
4655  // fds does not contain a valid month
4656  os.setstate(std::ios::failbit);
4657  return 0;
4658  }
4659  return static_cast<unsigned>(fds.ymd.month());
4660 }

4739 template <class CharT, class Traits, class FwdIter>
4740 FwdIter
4741 scan_keyword(std::basic_istream<CharT, Traits>& is, FwdIter kb, FwdIter ke)
4742 {
4743  size_t nkw = static_cast<size_t>(std::distance(kb, ke));
4744  const unsigned char doesnt_match = '\0';
4745  const unsigned char might_match = '\1';
4746  const unsigned char does_match = '\2';
4747  unsigned char statbuf[100];
4748  unsigned char* status = statbuf;
4749  std::unique_ptr<unsigned char, void(*)(void*)> stat_hold(0, free);
4750  if (nkw > sizeof(statbuf))
4751  {
4752  status = (unsigned char*)std::malloc(nkw);
4753  if (status == nullptr)
4754  throw std::bad_alloc();
4755  stat_hold.reset(status);
4756  }
4757  size_t n_might_match = nkw; // At this point, any keyword might match
4758  size_t n_does_match = 0; // but none of them definitely do
4759  // Initialize all statuses to might_match, except for "" keywords are does_match
4760  unsigned char* st = status;
4761  for (auto ky = kb; ky != ke; ++ky, ++st)
4762  {
4763  if (!ky->empty())
4764  *st = might_match;
4765  else
4766  {
4767  *st = does_match;
4768  --n_might_match;
4769  ++n_does_match;
4770  }
4771  }
4772  // While there might be a match, test keywords against the next CharT
4773  for (size_t indx = 0; is && n_might_match > 0; ++indx)
4774  {
4775  // Peek at the next CharT but don't consume it
4776  auto ic = is.peek();
4777  if (ic == EOF)
4778  {
4779  is.setstate(std::ios::eofbit);
4780  break;
4781  }
4782  auto c = static_cast<char>(toupper(ic));
4783  bool consume = false;
4784  // For each keyword which might match, see if the indx character is c
4785  // If a match if found, consume c
4786  // If a match is found, and that is the last character in the keyword,
4787  // then that keyword matches.
4788  // If the keyword doesn't match this character, then change the keyword
4789  // to doesn't match
4790  st = status;
4791  for (auto ky = kb; ky != ke; ++ky, ++st)
4792  {
4793  if (*st == might_match)
4794  {
4795  if (c == static_cast<char>(toupper((*ky)[indx])))
4796  {
4797  consume = true;
4798  if (ky->size() == indx+1)
4799  {
4800  *st = does_match;
4801  --n_might_match;
4802  ++n_does_match;
4803  }
4804  }
4805  else
4806  {
4807  *st = doesnt_match;
4808  --n_might_match;
4809  }
4810  }
4811  }
4812  // consume if we matched a character
4813  if (consume)
4814  {
4815  (void)is.get();
4816  // If we consumed a character and there might be a matched keyword that
4817  // was marked matched on a previous iteration, then such keywords
4818  // are now marked as not matching.
4819  if (n_might_match + n_does_match > 1)
4820  {
4821  st = status;
4822  for (auto ky = kb; ky != ke; ++ky, ++st)
4823  {
4824  if (*st == does_match && ky->size() != indx+1)
4825  {
4826  *st = doesnt_match;
4827  --n_does_match;
4828  }
4829  }
4830  }
4831  }
4832  }
4833  // We've exited the loop because we hit eof and/or we have no more "might matches".
4834  // Return the first matching result
4835  for (st = status; kb != ke; ++kb, ++st)
4836  if (*st == does_match)
4837  break;
4838  if (kb == ke)
4839  is.setstate(std::ios::failbit);
4840  return kb;
4841 }
4842 
4843 } // namespace detail

4845 #endif // ONLY_C_LOCALE
4846 
4847 template <class CharT, class Traits, class Duration>
4848 std::basic_ostream<CharT, Traits>&
4849 to_stream(std::basic_ostream<CharT, Traits>& os, const CharT* fmt,
4850  const fields<Duration>& fds, const std::string* abbrev,
4851  const std::chrono::seconds* offset_sec)
4852 {
4853 #if ONLY_C_LOCALE
4854  using detail::weekday_names;
4855  using detail::month_names;
4856  using detail::ampm_names;
4857 #endif
4858  using detail::save_ostream;
4859  using detail::get_units;
4860  using detail::extract_weekday;
4861  using detail::extract_month;
4862  using std::ios;
4863  using std::chrono::duration_cast;
4864  using std::chrono::seconds;
4865  using std::chrono::minutes;
4866  using std::chrono::hours;
4867  date::detail::save_ostream<CharT, Traits> ss(os);
4868  os.fill(' ');
4869  os.flags(std::ios::skipws | std::ios::dec);
4870  os.width(0);
4871  tm tm{};
4872  bool insert_negative = fds.has_tod && fds.tod.to_duration() < Duration::zero();
4873 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
4874  auto& facet = std::use_facet<std::time_put<CharT>>(os.getloc());
4875 #endif
4876  const CharT* command = nullptr;
4877  CharT modified = CharT{};
4878  for (; *fmt; ++fmt)
4879  {
4880  switch (*fmt)
4881  {
4882  case 'a':
4883  case 'A':
4884  if (command)
4885  {
4886  if (modified == CharT{})
4887  {
4888  tm.tm_wday = static_cast<int>(extract_weekday(os, fds));
4889  if (os.fail())
4890  return os;
4891 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
4892  const CharT f[] = {'%', *fmt};
4893  facet.put(os, os, os.fill(), &tm, std::begin(f), std::end(f));
4894 #else // ONLY_C_LOCALE
4895  os << weekday_names().first[tm.tm_wday+7*(*fmt == 'a')];
4896 #endif // ONLY_C_LOCALE
4897  }
4898  else
4899  {
4900  os << CharT{'%'} << modified << *fmt;
4901  modified = CharT{};
4902  }
4903  command = nullptr;
4904  }
4905  else
4906  os << *fmt;
4907  break;
4908  case 'b':
4909  case 'B':
4910  case 'h':
4911  if (command)
4912  {
4913  if (modified == CharT{})
4914  {
4915  tm.tm_mon = static_cast<int>(extract_month(os, fds)) - 1;
4916 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
4917  const CharT f[] = {'%', *fmt};
4918  facet.put(os, os, os.fill(), &tm, std::begin(f), std::end(f));
4919 #else // ONLY_C_LOCALE
4920  os << month_names().first[tm.tm_mon+12*(*fmt != 'B')];
4921 #endif // ONLY_C_LOCALE
4922  }
4923  else
4924  {
4925  os << CharT{'%'} << modified << *fmt;
4926  modified = CharT{};
4927  }
4928  command = nullptr;
4929  }
4930  else
4931  os << *fmt;
4932  break;
4933  case 'c':
4934  case 'x':
4935  if (command)
4936  {
4937  if (modified == CharT{'O'})
4938  os << CharT{'%'} << modified << *fmt;
4939  else
4940  {
4941  if (!fds.ymd.ok())
4942  os.setstate(std::ios::failbit);
4943  if (*fmt == 'c' && !fds.has_tod)
4944  os.setstate(std::ios::failbit);
4945 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
4946  tm = std::tm{};
4947  auto const& ymd = fds.ymd;
4948  auto ld = local_days(ymd);
4949  if (*fmt == 'c')
4950  {
4951  tm.tm_sec = static_cast<int>(fds.tod.seconds().count());
4952  tm.tm_min = static_cast<int>(fds.tod.minutes().count());
4953  tm.tm_hour = static_cast<int>(fds.tod.hours().count());
4954  }
4955  tm.tm_mday = static_cast<int>(static_cast<unsigned>(ymd.day()));
4956  tm.tm_mon = static_cast<int>(extract_month(os, fds) - 1);
4957  tm.tm_year = static_cast<int>(ymd.year()) - 1900;
4958  tm.tm_wday = static_cast<int>(extract_weekday(os, fds));
4959  if (os.fail())
4960  return os;
4961  tm.tm_yday = static_cast<int>((ld - local_days(ymd.year()/1/1)).count());
4962  CharT f[3] = {'%'};
4963  auto fe = std::begin(f) + 1;
4964  if (modified == CharT{'E'})
4965  *fe++ = modified;
4966  *fe++ = *fmt;
4967  facet.put(os, os, os.fill(), &tm, std::begin(f), fe);
4968 #else // ONLY_C_LOCALE
4969  if (*fmt == 'c')
4970  {
4971  auto wd = static_cast<int>(extract_weekday(os, fds));
4972  os << weekday_names().first[static_cast<unsigned>(wd)+7]
4973  << ' ';
4974  os << month_names().first[extract_month(os, fds)-1+12] << ' ';
4975  auto d = static_cast<int>(static_cast<unsigned>(fds.ymd.day()));
4976  if (d < 10)
4977  os << ' ';
4978  os << d << ' '
4979  << make_time(duration_cast<seconds>(fds.tod.to_duration()))
4980  << ' ' << fds.ymd.year();
4981 
4982  }
4983  else // *fmt == 'x'
4984  {
4985  auto const& ymd = fds.ymd;
4986  save_ostream<CharT, Traits> _(os);
4987  os.fill('0');
4988  os.flags(std::ios::dec | std::ios::right);
4989  os.width(2);
4990  os << static_cast<unsigned>(ymd.month()) << CharT{'/'};
4991  os.width(2);
4992  os << static_cast<unsigned>(ymd.day()) << CharT{'/'};
4993  os.width(2);
4994  os << static_cast<int>(ymd.year()) % 100;
4995  }
4996 #endif // ONLY_C_LOCALE
4997  }
4998  command = nullptr;
4999  modified = CharT{};
5000  }
5001  else
5002  os << *fmt;
5003  break;
5004  case 'C':
5005  if (command)
5006  {
5007  if (modified == CharT{'O'})
5008  os << CharT{'%'} << modified << *fmt;
5009  else
5010  {
5011  if (!fds.ymd.year().ok())
5012  os.setstate(std::ios::failbit);
5013  auto y = static_cast<int>(fds.ymd.year());
5014 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
5015  if (modified == CharT{})
5016 #endif
5017  {
5018  save_ostream<CharT, Traits> _(os);
5019  os.fill('0');
5020  os.flags(std::ios::dec | std::ios::right);
5021  if (y >= 0)
5022  {
5023  os.width(2);
5024  os << y/100;
5025  }
5026  else
5027  {
5028  os << CharT{'-'};
5029  os.width(2);
5030  os << -(y-99)/100;
5031  }
5032  }
5033 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
5034  else if (modified == CharT{'E'})
5035  {
5036  tm.tm_year = y - 1900;
5037  CharT f[3] = {'%', 'E', 'C'};
5038  facet.put(os, os, os.fill(), &tm, std::begin(f), std::end(f));
5039  }
5040 #endif
5041  }
5042  command = nullptr;
5043  modified = CharT{};
5044  }
5045  else
5046  os << *fmt;
5047  break;
5048  case 'd':
5049  case 'e':
5050  if (command)
5051  {
5052  if (modified == CharT{'E'})
5053  os << CharT{'%'} << modified << *fmt;
5054  else
5055  {
5056  if (!fds.ymd.day().ok())
5057  os.setstate(std::ios::failbit);
5058  auto d = static_cast<int>(static_cast<unsigned>(fds.ymd.day()));
5059 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
5060  if (modified == CharT{})
5061 #endif
5062  {
5063  save_ostream<CharT, Traits> _(os);
5064  if (*fmt == CharT{'d'})
5065  os.fill('0');
5066  else
5067  os.fill(' ');
5068  os.flags(std::ios::dec | std::ios::right);
5069  os.width(2);
5070  os << d;
5071  }
5072 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
5073  else if (modified == CharT{'O'})
5074  {
5075  tm.tm_mday = d;
5076  CharT f[3] = {'%', 'O', *fmt};
5077  facet.put(os, os, os.fill(), &tm, std::begin(f), std::end(f));
5078  }
5079 #endif
5080  }
5081  command = nullptr;
5082  modified = CharT{};
5083  }
5084  else
5085  os << *fmt;
5086  break;
5087  case 'D':
5088  if (command)
5089  {
5090  if (modified == CharT{})
5091  {
5092  if (!fds.ymd.ok())
5093  os.setstate(std::ios::failbit);
5094  auto const& ymd = fds.ymd;
5095  save_ostream<CharT, Traits> _(os);
5096  os.fill('0');
5097  os.flags(std::ios::dec | std::ios::right);
5098  os.width(2);
5099  os << static_cast<unsigned>(ymd.month()) << CharT{'/'};
5100  os.width(2);
5101  os << static_cast<unsigned>(ymd.day()) << CharT{'/'};
5102  os.width(2);
5103  os << static_cast<int>(ymd.year()) % 100;
5104  }
5105  else
5106  {
5107  os << CharT{'%'} << modified << *fmt;
5108  modified = CharT{};
5109  }
5110  command = nullptr;
5111  }
5112  else
5113  os << *fmt;
5114  break;
5115  case 'F':
5116  if (command)
5117  {
5118  if (modified == CharT{})
5119  {
5120  if (!fds.ymd.ok())
5121  os.setstate(std::ios::failbit);
5122  auto const& ymd = fds.ymd;
5123  save_ostream<CharT, Traits> _(os);
5124  os.imbue(std::locale::classic());
5125  os.fill('0');
5126  os.flags(std::ios::dec | std::ios::right);
5127  os.width(4);
5128  os << static_cast<int>(ymd.year()) << CharT{'-'};
5129  os.width(2);
5130  os << static_cast<unsigned>(ymd.month()) << CharT{'-'};
5131  os.width(2);
5132  os << static_cast<unsigned>(ymd.day());
5133  }
5134  else
5135  {
5136  os << CharT{'%'} << modified << *fmt;
5137  modified = CharT{};
5138  }
5139  command = nullptr;
5140  }
5141  else
5142  os << *fmt;
5143  break;
5144  case 'g':
5145  case 'G':
5146  if (command)
5147  {
5148  if (modified == CharT{})
5149  {
5150  if (!fds.ymd.ok())
5151  os.setstate(std::ios::failbit);
5152  auto ld = local_days(fds.ymd);
5153  auto y = year_month_day{ld + days{3}}.year();
5154  auto start = local_days((y-years{1})/December/Thursday[last]) +
5155  (Monday-Thursday);
5156  if (ld < start)
5157  --y;
5158  if (*fmt == CharT{'G'})
5159  os << y;
5160  else
5161  {
5162  save_ostream<CharT, Traits> _(os);
5163  os.fill('0');
5164  os.flags(std::ios::dec | std::ios::right);
5165  os.width(2);
5166  os << std::abs(static_cast<int>(y)) % 100;
5167  }
5168  }
5169  else
5170  {
5171  os << CharT{'%'} << modified << *fmt;
5172  modified = CharT{};
5173  }
5174  command = nullptr;
5175  }
5176  else
5177  os << *fmt;
5178  break;
5179  case 'H':
5180  case 'I':
5181  if (command)
5182  {
5183  if (modified == CharT{'E'})
5184  os << CharT{'%'} << modified << *fmt;
5185  else
5186  {
5187  if (!fds.has_tod)
5188  os.setstate(std::ios::failbit);
5189  if (insert_negative)
5190  {
5191  os << '-';
5192  insert_negative = false;
5193  }
5194  auto hms = fds.tod;
5195 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
5196  if (modified == CharT{})
5197 #endif
5198  {
5199  auto h = *fmt == CharT{'I'} ? date::make12(hms.hours()) : hms.hours();
5200  if (h < hours{10})
5201  os << CharT{'0'};
5202  os << h.count();
5203  }
5204 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
5205  else if (modified == CharT{'O'})
5206  {
5207  const CharT f[] = {'%', modified, *fmt};
5208  tm.tm_hour = static_cast<int>(hms.hours().count());
5209  facet.put(os, os, os.fill(), &tm, std::begin(f), std::end(f));
5210  }
5211 #endif
5212  }
5213  modified = CharT{};
5214  command = nullptr;
5215  }
5216  else
5217  os << *fmt;
5218  break;
5219  case 'j':
5220  if (command)
5221  {
5222  if (modified == CharT{})
5223  {
5224  if (fds.ymd.ok() || fds.has_tod)
5225  {
5226  days doy;
5227  if (fds.ymd.ok())
5228  {
5229  auto ld = local_days(fds.ymd);
5230  auto y = fds.ymd.year();
5231  doy = ld - local_days(y/January/1) + days{1};
5232  }
5233  else
5234  {
5235  doy = duration_cast<days>(fds.tod.to_duration());
5236  }
5237  save_ostream<CharT, Traits> _(os);
5238  os.fill('0');
5239  os.flags(std::ios::dec | std::ios::right);
5240  os.width(3);
5241  os << doy.count();
5242  }
5243  else
5244  {
5245  os.setstate(std::ios::failbit);
5246  }
5247  }
5248  else
5249  {
5250  os << CharT{'%'} << modified << *fmt;
5251  modified = CharT{};
5252  }
5253  command = nullptr;
5254  }
5255  else
5256  os << *fmt;
5257  break;
5258  case 'm':
5259  if (command)
5260  {
5261  if (modified == CharT{'E'})
5262  os << CharT{'%'} << modified << *fmt;
5263  else
5264  {
5265  if (!fds.ymd.month().ok())
5266  os.setstate(std::ios::failbit);
5267  auto m = static_cast<unsigned>(fds.ymd.month());
5268 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
5269  if (modified == CharT{})
5270 #endif
5271  {

5273  os << CharT{'0'};
5274  os << m;
5275  }
5276 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE

5278  {

5280  tm.tm_mon = static_cast<int>(m-1);
5281  facet.put(os, os, os.fill(), &tm, std::begin(f), std::end(f));
5282  }
5283 #endif

5285  modified = CharT{};
5286  command = nullptr;

5296  else

5300  if (insert_negative)

5320 #endif
5321  }

5328  case 'n':

5529  {
5530  if (modified == CharT{'E'})
5531  os << CharT{'%'} << modified << *fmt;
5532  else
5533  {
5534  auto wd = extract_weekday(os, fds);
5535 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
5536  if (modified == CharT{})
5537 #endif
5538  {
5539  os << (wd != 0 ? wd : 7u);
5540  }
5541 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
5542  else if (modified == CharT{'O'})
5543  {
5544  const CharT f[] = {'%', modified, *fmt};
5545  tm.tm_wday = static_cast<int>(wd);
5546  facet.put(os, os, os.fill(), &tm, std::begin(f), std::end(f));
5547  }
5548 #endif
5549  }
5550  modified = CharT{};
5551  command = nullptr;
5552  }
5553  else
5554  os << *fmt;
5555  break;
5556  case 'U':
5557  if (command)
5558  {
5559  if (modified == CharT{'E'})
5560  os << CharT{'%'} << modified << *fmt;
5561  else
5562  {
5563  auto const& ymd = fds.ymd;
5564  if (!ymd.ok())
5565  os.setstate(std::ios::failbit);
5566  auto ld = local_days(ymd);
5567 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
5568  if (modified == CharT{})
5569 #endif
5570  {
5571  auto st = local_days(Sunday[1]/January/ymd.year());
5572  if (ld < st)
5573  os << CharT{'0'} << CharT{'0'};
5574  else
5575  {
5576  auto wn = duration_cast<weeks>(ld - st).count() + 1;
5577  if (wn < 10)
5578  os << CharT{'0'};
5579  os << wn;
5580  }
5581  }
5582  #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
5583  else if (modified == CharT{'O'})
5584  {
5585  const CharT f[] = {'%', modified, *fmt};
5586  tm.tm_year = static_cast<int>(ymd.year()) - 1900;
5587  tm.tm_wday = static_cast<int>(extract_weekday(os, fds));
5588  if (os.fail())
5589  return os;
5590  tm.tm_yday = static_cast<int>((ld - local_days(ymd.year()/1/1)).count());
5591  facet.put(os, os, os.fill(), &tm, std::begin(f), std::end(f));
5592  }
5593 #endif
5594  }
5595  modified = CharT{};
5596  command = nullptr;
5597  }
5598  else
5599  os << *fmt;
5600  break;
5601  case 'V':
5602  if (command)
5603  {
5604  if (modified == CharT{'E'})
5605  os << CharT{'%'} << modified << *fmt;
5606  else
5607  {
5608  if (!fds.ymd.ok())
5609  os.setstate(std::ios::failbit);
5610  auto ld = local_days(fds.ymd);
5611 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
5612  if (modified == CharT{})
5613 #endif
5614  {
5615  auto y = year_month_day{ld + days{3}}.year();
5616  auto st = local_days((y-years{1})/12/Thursday[last]) +
5617  (Monday-Thursday);
5618  if (ld < st)
5619  {
5620  --y;
5621  st = local_days((y - years{1})/12/Thursday[last]) +
5622  (Monday-Thursday);
5623  }
5624  auto wn = duration_cast<weeks>(ld - st).count() + 1;
5625  if (wn < 10)
5626  os << CharT{'0'};
5627  os << wn;
5628  }
5629 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
5630  else if (modified == CharT{'O'})
5631  {
5632  const CharT f[] = {'%', modified, *fmt};
5633  auto const& ymd = fds.ymd;
5634  tm.tm_year = static_cast<int>(ymd.year()) - 1900;
5635  tm.tm_wday = static_cast<int>(extract_weekday(os, fds));
5636  if (os.fail())
5637  return os;
5638  tm.tm_yday = static_cast<int>((ld - local_days(ymd.year()/1/1)).count());
5639  facet.put(os, os, os.fill(), &tm, std::begin(f), std::end(f));
5640  }
5641 #endif
5642  }
5643  modified = CharT{};
5644  command = nullptr;
5645  }
5646  else
5647  os << *fmt;
5648  break;
5649  case 'w':
5650  if (command)
5651  {
5652  auto wd = extract_weekday(os, fds);
5653  if (os.fail())
5654  return os;
5655 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
5656  if (modified == CharT{})
5657 #else
5658  if (modified != CharT{'E'})
5659 #endif
5660  {
5661  os << wd;
5662  }
5663 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
5664  else if (modified == CharT{'O'})
5665  {
5666  const CharT f[] = {'%', modified, *fmt};
5667  tm.tm_wday = static_cast<int>(wd);
5668  facet.put(os, os, os.fill(), &tm, std::begin(f), std::end(f));
5669  }
5670 #endif
5671  else
5672  {
5673  os << CharT{'%'} << modified << *fmt;
5674  }
5675  modified = CharT{};
5676  command = nullptr;
5677  }
5678  else
5679  os << *fmt;
5680  break;
5681  case 'W':
5682  if (command)
5683  {
5684  if (modified == CharT{'E'})
5685  os << CharT{'%'} << modified << *fmt;
5686  else
5687  {
5688  auto const& ymd = fds.ymd;
5689  if (!ymd.ok())
5690  os.setstate(std::ios::failbit);
5691  auto ld = local_days(ymd);
5692 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
5693  if (modified == CharT{})
5694 #endif
5695  {
5696  auto st = local_days(Monday[1]/January/ymd.year());
5697  if (ld < st)
5698  os << CharT{'0'} << CharT{'0'};
5699  else
5700  {
5701  auto wn = duration_cast<weeks>(ld - st).count() + 1;
5702  if (wn < 10)
5703  os << CharT{'0'};
5704  os << wn;
5705  }
5706  }
5707 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
5708  else if (modified == CharT{'O'})
5709  {
5710  const CharT f[] = {'%', modified, *fmt};
5711  tm.tm_year = static_cast<int>(ymd.year()) - 1900;
5712  tm.tm_wday = static_cast<int>(extract_weekday(os, fds));
5713  if (os.fail())
5714  return os;
5715  tm.tm_yday = static_cast<int>((ld - local_days(ymd.year()/1/1)).count());
5716  facet.put(os, os, os.fill(), &tm, std::begin(f), std::end(f));
5717  }
5718 #endif
5719  }
5720  modified = CharT{};
5721  command = nullptr;
5722  }
5723  else
5724  os << *fmt;
5725  break;
5726  case 'X':
5727  if (command)
5728  {
5729  if (modified == CharT{'O'})
5730  os << CharT{'%'} << modified << *fmt;
5731  else
5732  {
5733  if (!fds.has_tod)
5734  os.setstate(std::ios::failbit);
5735 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
5736  tm = std::tm{};
5737  tm.tm_sec = static_cast<int>(fds.tod.seconds().count());
5738  tm.tm_min = static_cast<int>(fds.tod.minutes().count());
5739  tm.tm_hour = static_cast<int>(fds.tod.hours().count());
5740  CharT f[3] = {'%'};
5741  auto fe = std::begin(f) + 1;
5742  if (modified == CharT{'E'})
5743  *fe++ = modified;
5744  *fe++ = *fmt;
5745  facet.put(os, os, os.fill(), &tm, std::begin(f), fe);
5746 #else
5747  os << fds.tod;
5748 #endif
5749  }
5750  command = nullptr;
5751  modified = CharT{};
5752  }
5753  else
5754  os << *fmt;
5755  break;
5756  case 'y':
5757  if (command)
5758  {
5759  if (!fds.ymd.year().ok())
5760  os.setstate(std::ios::failbit);
5761  auto y = static_cast<int>(fds.ymd.year());
5762 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
5763  if (modified == CharT{})
5764  {
5765 #endif
5766  y = std::abs(y) % 100;
5767  if (y < 10)
5768  os << CharT{'0'};
5769  os << y;
5770 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
5771  }
5772  else
5773  {
5774  const CharT f[] = {'%', modified, *fmt};
5775  tm.tm_year = y - 1900;
5776  facet.put(os, os, os.fill(), &tm, std::begin(f), std::end(f));
5777  }
5778 #endif
5779  modified = CharT{};
5780  command = nullptr;
5781  }
5782  else
5783  os << *fmt;
5784  break;
5785  case 'Y':
5786  if (command)
5787  {
5788  if (modified == CharT{'O'})
5789  os << CharT{'%'} << modified << *fmt;
5790  else
5791  {
5792  if (!fds.ymd.year().ok())
5793  os.setstate(std::ios::failbit);
5794  auto y = fds.ymd.year();
5795 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
5796  if (modified == CharT{})
5797 #endif
5798  {
5799  save_ostream<CharT, Traits> _(os);
5800  os.imbue(std::locale::classic());
5801  os << y;
5802  }
5803 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
5804  else if (modified == CharT{'E'})
5805  {
5806  const CharT f[] = {'%', modified, *fmt};
5807  tm.tm_year = static_cast<int>(y) - 1900;
5808  facet.put(os, os, os.fill(), &tm, std::begin(f), std::end(f));
5809  }
5810 #endif
5811  }
5812  modified = CharT{};
5813  command = nullptr;
5814  }
5815  else
5816  os << *fmt;
5817  break;
5818  case 'z':
5819  if (command)
5820  {
5821  if (offset_sec == nullptr)
5822  {
5823  // Can not format %z with unknown offset
5824  os.setstate(ios::failbit);
5825  return os;
5826  }
5827  auto m = duration_cast<minutes>(*offset_sec);
5828  auto neg = m < minutes{0};
5829  m = date::abs(m);
5830  auto h = duration_cast<hours>(m);
5831  m -= h;
5832  if (neg)
5833  os << CharT{'-'};
5834  else
5835  os << CharT{'+'};
5836  if (h < hours{10})
5837  os << CharT{'0'};
5838  os << h.count();
5839  if (modified != CharT{})
5840  os << CharT{':'};
5841  if (m < minutes{10})
5842  os << CharT{'0'};
5843  os << m.count();
5844  command = nullptr;
5845  modified = CharT{};
5846  }
5847  else
5848  os << *fmt;
5849  break;
5850  case 'Z':
5851  if (command)
5852  {
5853  if (modified == CharT{})
5854  {
5855  if (abbrev == nullptr)
5856  {
5857  // Can not format %Z with unknown time_zone
5858  os.setstate(ios::failbit);
5859  return os;
5860  }
5861  for (auto c : *abbrev)
5862  os << CharT(c);
5863  }
5864  else
5865  {
5866  os << CharT{'%'} << modified << *fmt;
5867  modified = CharT{};
5868  }
5869  command = nullptr;
5870  }
5871  else
5872  os << *fmt;
5873  break;
5874  case 'E':
5875  case 'O':
5876  if (command)
5877  {
5878  if (modified == CharT{})
5879  {
5880  modified = *fmt;
5881  }
5882  else
5883  {
5884  os << CharT{'%'} << modified << *fmt;
5885  command = nullptr;
5886  modified = CharT{};
5887  }
5888  }
5889  else
5890  os << *fmt;
5891  break;
5892  case '%':
5893  if (command)
5894  {
5895  if (modified == CharT{})
5896  {
5897  os << CharT{'%'};
5898  command = nullptr;
5899  }
5900  else
5901  {
5902  os << CharT{'%'} << modified << CharT{'%'};
5903  command = nullptr;
5904  modified = CharT{};
5905  }
5906  }
5907  else
5908  command = fmt;
5909  break;
5910  default:
5911  if (command)
5912  {
5913  os << CharT{'%'};
5914  command = nullptr;
5915  }
5916  if (modified != CharT{})
5917  {
5918  os << modified;
5919  modified = CharT{};
5920  }
5921  os << *fmt;
5922  break;
5923  }
5924  }
5925  if (command)
5926  os << CharT{'%'};
5927  if (modified != CharT{})
5928  os << modified;
5929  return os;
5930 }

6003 template <class CharT, class Traits, class Rep, class Period>
6004 inline
6005 std::basic_ostream<CharT, Traits>&
6006 to_stream(std::basic_ostream<CharT, Traits>& os, const CharT* fmt,
6007  const std::chrono::duration<Rep, Period>& d)
6008 {
6009  using Duration = std::chrono::duration<Rep, Period>;
6010  using CT = typename std::common_type<Duration, std::chrono::seconds>::type;
6011  fields<CT> fds{hh_mm_ss<CT>{d}};
6012  return to_stream(os, fmt, fds);
6013 }

6015 template <class CharT, class Traits, class Duration>
6016 std::basic_ostream<CharT, Traits>&
6017 to_stream(std::basic_ostream<CharT, Traits>& os, const CharT* fmt,
6018  const local_time<Duration>& tp, const std::string* abbrev = nullptr,
6019  const std::chrono::seconds* offset_sec = nullptr)
6020 {
6021  using CT = typename std::common_type<Duration, std::chrono::seconds>::type;
6022  auto ld = floor<days>(tp);
6023  fields<CT> fds{year_month_day{ld}, hh_mm_ss<CT>{tp-local_seconds{ld}}};
6024  return to_stream(os, fmt, fds, abbrev, offset_sec);
6025 }

6027 template <class CharT, class Traits, class Duration>
6028 std::basic_ostream<CharT, Traits>&
6029 to_stream(std::basic_ostream<CharT, Traits>& os, const CharT* fmt,
6030  const sys_time<Duration>& tp)
6031 {
6032  using std::chrono::seconds;
6033  using CT = typename std::common_type<Duration, seconds>::type;
6034  const std::string abbrev("UTC");
6035  CONSTDATA seconds offset{0};
6036  auto sd = floor<days>(tp);
6037  fields<CT> fds{year_month_day{sd}, hh_mm_ss<CT>{tp-sys_seconds{sd}}};
6038  return to_stream(os, fmt, fds, &abbrev, &offset);
6039 }

6045 format(const std::locale& loc, const CharT* fmt, const Streamable& tp)
6046  -> decltype(to_stream(std::declval<std::basic_ostream<CharT>&>(), fmt, tp),
6047  std::basic_string<CharT>{})
6048 {

6050  os.exceptions(std::ios::failbit | std::ios::badbit);
6051  os.imbue(loc);
6052  to_stream(os, fmt, tp);
6053  return os.str();

6096 namespace detail
6097 {
6098 
6099 template <class CharT, class Traits>
6100 bool
6101 read_char(std::basic_istream<CharT, Traits>& is, CharT fmt, std::ios::iostate& err)
6102 {
6103  auto ic = is.get();
6104  if (Traits::eq_int_type(ic, Traits::eof()) ||
6105  !Traits::eq(Traits::to_char_type(ic), fmt))
6106  {
6107  err |= std::ios::failbit;
6108  is.setstate(std::ios::failbit);
6109  return false;
6110  }
6111  return true;
6112 }
6113 
6114 template <class CharT, class Traits>
6115 unsigned
6116 read_unsigned(std::basic_istream<CharT, Traits>& is, unsigned m = 1, unsigned M = 10)
6117 {
6118  unsigned x = 0;
6119  unsigned count = 0;
6120  while (true)
6121  {
6122  auto ic = is.peek();
6123  if (Traits::eq_int_type(ic, Traits::eof()))
6124  break;
6125  auto c = static_cast<char>(Traits::to_char_type(ic));
6126  if (!('0' <= c && c <= '9'))
6127  break;
6128  (void)is.get();
6129  ++count;
6130  x = 10*x + static_cast<unsigned>(c - '0');
6131  if (count == M)
6132  break;
6133  }
6134  if (count < m)
6135  is.setstate(std::ios::failbit);
6136  return x;
6137 }
6138 
6139 template <class CharT, class Traits>
6140 int
6141 read_signed(std::basic_istream<CharT, Traits>& is, unsigned m = 1, unsigned M = 10)
6142 {
6143  auto ic = is.peek();
6144  if (!Traits::eq_int_type(ic, Traits::eof()))
6145  {
6146  auto c = static_cast<char>(Traits::to_char_type(ic));
6147  if (('0' <= c && c <= '9') || c == '-' || c == '+')
6148  {
6149  if (c == '-' || c == '+')
6150  (void)is.get();
6151  auto x = static_cast<int>(read_unsigned(is, std::max(m, 1u), M));
6152  if (!is.fail())
6153  {
6154  if (c == '-')
6155  x = -x;
6156  return x;
6157  }
6158  }
6159  }
6160  if (m > 0)
6161  is.setstate(std::ios::failbit);
6162  return 0;
6163 }
6164 
6165 template <class CharT, class Traits>
6166 long double
6167 read_long_double(std::basic_istream<CharT, Traits>& is, unsigned m = 1, unsigned M = 10)
6168 {
6169  unsigned count = 0;
6170  unsigned fcount = 0;
6171  unsigned long long i = 0;
6172  unsigned long long f = 0;
6173  bool parsing_fraction = false;
6174 #if ONLY_C_LOCALE
6175  typename Traits::int_type decimal_point = '.';
6176 #else
6177  auto decimal_point = Traits::to_int_type(
6178  std::use_facet<std::numpunct<CharT>>(is.getloc()).decimal_point());
6179 #endif
6180  while (true)
6181  {
6182  auto ic = is.peek();
6183  if (Traits::eq_int_type(ic, Traits::eof()))
6184  break;
6185  if (Traits::eq_int_type(ic, decimal_point))
6186  {
6187  decimal_point = Traits::eof();
6188  parsing_fraction = true;
6189  }
6190  else
6191  {
6192  auto c = static_cast<char>(Traits::to_char_type(ic));
6193  if (!('0' <= c && c <= '9'))
6194  break;
6195  if (!parsing_fraction)
6196  {
6197  i = 10*i + static_cast<unsigned>(c - '0');
6198  }
6199  else
6200  {
6201  f = 10*f + static_cast<unsigned>(c - '0');
6202  ++fcount;
6203  }
6204  }
6205  (void)is.get();
6206  if (++count == M)
6207  break;
6208  }
6209  if (count < m)
6210  {
6211  is.setstate(std::ios::failbit);
6212  return 0;
6213  }
6214  return i + f/std::pow(10.L, fcount);
6215 }
6216 
6217 struct rs
6218 {
6219  int& i;
6220  unsigned m;
6221  unsigned M;
6222 };
6223 
6224 struct ru
6225 {
6226  int& i;
6227  unsigned m;
6228  unsigned M;
6229 };
6230 
6231 struct rld
6232 {
6233  long double& i;
6234  unsigned m;
6235  unsigned M;
6236 };

6263 
6264 template <class CharT, class Traits, class ...Args>
6265 void
6266 read(std::basic_istream<CharT, Traits>& is, CharT a0, Args&& ...args)
6267 {
6268  // No-op if a0 == CharT{}
6269  if (a0 != CharT{})
6270  {
6271  auto ic = is.peek();
6272  if (Traits::eq_int_type(ic, Traits::eof()))
6273  {
6274  is.setstate(std::ios::failbit | std::ios::eofbit);
6275  return;
6276  }
6277  if (!Traits::eq(Traits::to_char_type(ic), a0))
6278  {
6279  is.setstate(std::ios::failbit);
6280  return;
6281  }
6282  (void)is.get();
6283  }
6284  read(is, std::forward<Args>(args)...);
6285 }
6286 
6287 template <class CharT, class Traits, class ...Args>
6288 void
6289 read(std::basic_istream<CharT, Traits>& is, rs a0, Args&& ...args)
6290 {
6291  auto x = read_signed(is, a0.m, a0.M);
6292  if (is.fail())
6293  return;
6294  a0.i = x;
6295  read(is, std::forward<Args>(args)...);
6296 }
6297 
6298 template <class CharT, class Traits, class ...Args>
6299 void
6300 read(std::basic_istream<CharT, Traits>& is, ru a0, Args&& ...args)
6301 {
6302  auto x = read_unsigned(is, a0.m, a0.M);
6303  if (is.fail())
6304  return;
6305  a0.i = static_cast<int>(x);
6306  read(is, std::forward<Args>(args)...);
6307 }
6308 
6309 template <class CharT, class Traits, class ...Args>
6310 void
6311 read(std::basic_istream<CharT, Traits>& is, int a0, Args&& ...args)
6312 {
6313  if (a0 != -1)
6314  {
6315  auto u = static_cast<unsigned>(a0);
6316  CharT buf[std::numeric_limits<unsigned>::digits10+2u] = {};
6317  auto e = buf;
6318  do
6319  {
6320  *e++ = static_cast<CharT>(CharT(u % 10) + CharT{'0'});
6321  u /= 10;
6322  } while (u > 0);
6323  std::reverse(buf, e);
6324  for (auto p = buf; p != e && is.rdstate() == std::ios::goodbit; ++p)
6325  read(is, *p);
6326  }
6327  if (is.rdstate() == std::ios::goodbit)
6328  read(is, std::forward<Args>(args)...);
6329 }
6330 
6331 template <class CharT, class Traits, class ...Args>
6332 void
6333 read(std::basic_istream<CharT, Traits>& is, rld a0, Args&& ...args)
6334 {
6335  auto x = read_long_double(is, a0.m, a0.M);
6336  if (is.fail())
6337  return;
6338  a0.i = x;
6339  read(is, std::forward<Args>(args)...);
6340 }
6341 
6342 template <class T, class CharT, class Traits>
6343 inline
6344 void
6345 checked_set(T& value, T from, T not_a_value, std::basic_ios<CharT, Traits>& is)
6346 {
6347  if (!is.fail())
6348  {
6349  if (value == not_a_value)
6350  value = std::move(from);
6351  else if (value != from)
6352  is.setstate(std::ios::failbit);
6353  }
6354 }
6355 
6356 } // namespace detail;
6357 
6358 template <class CharT, class Traits, class Duration, class Alloc = std::allocator<CharT>>
6359 std::basic_istream<CharT, Traits>&
6360 from_stream(std::basic_istream<CharT, Traits>& is, const CharT* fmt,
6361  fields<Duration>& fds, std::basic_string<CharT, Traits, Alloc>* abbrev,
6362  std::chrono::minutes* offset)
6363 {
6364  using std::numeric_limits;
6365  using std::ios;
6366  using std::chrono::duration;
6367  using std::chrono::duration_cast;
6368  using std::chrono::seconds;
6369  using std::chrono::minutes;
6370  using std::chrono::hours;
6371  using detail::round_i;
6372  typename std::basic_istream<CharT, Traits>::sentry ok{is, true};
6373  if (ok)
6374  {
6375  date::detail::save_istream<CharT, Traits> ss(is);
6376  is.fill(' ');
6377  is.flags(std::ios::skipws | std::ios::dec);
6378  is.width(0);
6379 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
6380  auto& f = std::use_facet<std::time_get<CharT>>(is.getloc());
6381  std::tm tm{};
6382 #endif
6383  const CharT* command = nullptr;
6384  auto modified = CharT{};
6385  auto width = -1;
6386 
6387  CONSTDATA int not_a_year = numeric_limits<short>::min();
6388  CONSTDATA int not_a_2digit_year = 100;
6389  CONSTDATA int not_a_century = not_a_year / 100;
6390  CONSTDATA int not_a_month = 0;
6391  CONSTDATA int not_a_day = 0;
6392  CONSTDATA int not_a_hour = numeric_limits<int>::min();
6393  CONSTDATA int not_a_hour_12_value = 0;
6394  CONSTDATA int not_a_minute = not_a_hour;
6395  CONSTDATA Duration not_a_second = Duration::min();
6396  CONSTDATA int not_a_doy = -1;
6397  CONSTDATA int not_a_weekday = 8;
6398  CONSTDATA int not_a_week_num = 100;
6399  CONSTDATA int not_a_ampm = -1;
6400  CONSTDATA minutes not_a_offset = minutes::min();
6401 
6402  int Y = not_a_year; // c, F, Y *
6403  int y = not_a_2digit_year; // D, x, y *
6404  int g = not_a_2digit_year; // g *
6405  int G = not_a_year; // G *
6406  int C = not_a_century; // C *
6407  int m = not_a_month; // b, B, h, m, c, D, F, x *
6408  int d = not_a_day; // c, d, D, e, F, x *
6409  int j = not_a_doy; // j *
6410  int wd = not_a_weekday; // a, A, u, w *
6411  int H = not_a_hour; // c, H, R, T, X *
6412  int I = not_a_hour_12_value; // I, r *
6413  int p = not_a_ampm; // p, r *
6414  int M = not_a_minute; // c, M, r, R, T, X *
6415  Duration s = not_a_second; // c, r, S, T, X *
6416  int U = not_a_week_num; // U *
6417  int V = not_a_week_num; // V *
6418  int W = not_a_week_num; // W *
6419  std::basic_string<CharT, Traits, Alloc> temp_abbrev; // Z *
6420  minutes temp_offset = not_a_offset; // z *
6421 
6422  using detail::read;
6423  using detail::rs;
6424  using detail::ru;
6425  using detail::rld;
6426  using detail::checked_set;
6427  for (; *fmt != CharT{} && !is.fail(); ++fmt)
6428  {
6429  switch (*fmt)
6430  {
6431  case 'a':
6432  case 'A':
6433  case 'u':
6434  case 'w': // wd: a, A, u, w
6435  if (command)
6436  {
6437  int trial_wd = not_a_weekday;
6438  if (*fmt == 'a' || *fmt == 'A')
6439  {
6440  if (modified == CharT{})
6441  {
6442 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
6443  ios::iostate err = ios::goodbit;
6444  f.get(is, nullptr, is, err, &tm, command, fmt+1);
6445  is.setstate(err);
6446  if (!is.fail())
6447  trial_wd = tm.tm_wday;
6448 #else
6449  auto nm = detail::weekday_names();
6450  auto i = detail::scan_keyword(is, nm.first, nm.second) - nm.first;
6451  if (!is.fail())
6452  trial_wd = i % 7;
6453 #endif
6454  }
6455  else
6456  read(is, CharT{'%'}, width, modified, *fmt);
6457  }
6458  else // *fmt == 'u' || *fmt == 'w'
6459  {
6460 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
6461  if (modified == CharT{})
6462 #else
6463  if (modified != CharT{'E'})
6464 #endif
6465  {
6466  read(is, ru{trial_wd, 1, width == -1 ?
6467  1u : static_cast<unsigned>(width)});
6468  if (!is.fail())
6469  {
6470  if (*fmt == 'u')
6471  {
6472  if (!(1 <= trial_wd && trial_wd <= 7))
6473  {
6474  trial_wd = not_a_weekday;
6475  is.setstate(ios::failbit);
6476  }
6477  else if (trial_wd == 7)
6478  trial_wd = 0;
6479  }
6480  else // *fmt == 'w'
6481  {
6482  if (!(0 <= trial_wd && trial_wd <= 6))
6483  {
6484  trial_wd = not_a_weekday;
6485  is.setstate(ios::failbit);
6486  }
6487  }
6488  }
6489  }
6490 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
6491  else if (modified == CharT{'O'})
6492  {
6493  ios::iostate err = ios::goodbit;
6494  f.get(is, nullptr, is, err, &tm, command, fmt+1);
6495  is.setstate(err);
6496  if (!is.fail())
6497  trial_wd = tm.tm_wday;
6498  }
6499 #endif
6500  else
6501  read(is, CharT{'%'}, width, modified, *fmt);
6502  }
6503  if (trial_wd != not_a_weekday)
6504  checked_set(wd, trial_wd, not_a_weekday, is);
6505  }
6506  else // !command
6507  read(is, *fmt);
6508  command = nullptr;
6509  width = -1;
6510  modified = CharT{};
6511  break;
6512  case 'b':
6513  case 'B':
6514  case 'h':
6515  if (command)
6516  {
6517  if (modified == CharT{})
6518  {
6519  int ttm = not_a_month;
6520 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
6521  ios::iostate err = ios::goodbit;
6522  f.get(is, nullptr, is, err, &tm, command, fmt+1);
6523  if ((err & ios::failbit) == 0)
6524  ttm = tm.tm_mon + 1;
6525  is.setstate(err);
6526 #else
6527  auto nm = detail::month_names();
6528  auto i = detail::scan_keyword(is, nm.first, nm.second) - nm.first;
6529  if (!is.fail())
6530  ttm = i % 12 + 1;
6531 #endif
6532  checked_set(m, ttm, not_a_month, is);
6533  }
6534  else
6535  read(is, CharT{'%'}, width, modified, *fmt);
6536  command = nullptr;
6537  width = -1;
6538  modified = CharT{};
6539  }
6540  else
6541  read(is, *fmt);
6542  break;
6543  case 'c':
6544  if (command)
6545  {
6546  if (modified != CharT{'O'})
6547  {
6548 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
6549  ios::iostate err = ios::goodbit;
6550  f.get(is, nullptr, is, err, &tm, command, fmt+1);
6551  if ((err & ios::failbit) == 0)
6552  {
6553  checked_set(Y, tm.tm_year + 1900, not_a_year, is);
6554  checked_set(m, tm.tm_mon + 1, not_a_month, is);
6555  checked_set(d, tm.tm_mday, not_a_day, is);
6556  checked_set(H, tm.tm_hour, not_a_hour, is);
6557  checked_set(M, tm.tm_min, not_a_minute, is);
6558  checked_set(s, duration_cast<Duration>(seconds{tm.tm_sec}),
6559  not_a_second, is);
6560  }
6561  is.setstate(err);
6562 #else
6563  // "%a %b %e %T %Y"
6564  auto nm = detail::weekday_names();
6565  auto i = detail::scan_keyword(is, nm.first, nm.second) - nm.first;
6566  checked_set(wd, static_cast<int>(i % 7), not_a_weekday, is);
6567  ws(is);
6568  nm = detail::month_names();
6569  i = detail::scan_keyword(is, nm.first, nm.second) - nm.first;
6570  checked_set(m, static_cast<int>(i % 12 + 1), not_a_month, is);
6571  ws(is);
6572  int td = not_a_day;
6573  read(is, rs{td, 1, 2});
6574  checked_set(d, td, not_a_day, is);
6575  ws(is);
6576  using dfs = detail::decimal_format_seconds<Duration>;
6577  CONSTDATA auto w = Duration::period::den == 1 ? 2 : 3 + dfs::width;
6578  int tH;
6579  int tM;
6580  long double S;
6581  read(is, ru{tH, 1, 2}, CharT{':'}, ru{tM, 1, 2},
6582  CharT{':'}, rld{S, 1, w});
6583  checked_set(H, tH, not_a_hour, is);
6584  checked_set(M, tM, not_a_minute, is);
6585  checked_set(s, round_i<Duration>(duration<long double>{S}),
6586  not_a_second, is);
6587  ws(is);
6588  int tY = not_a_year;
6589  read(is, rs{tY, 1, 4u});
6590  checked_set(Y, tY, not_a_year, is);
6591 #endif
6592  }
6593  else
6594  read(is, CharT{'%'}, width, modified, *fmt);
6595  command = nullptr;
6596  width = -1;
6597  modified = CharT{};
6598  }
6599  else
6600  read(is, *fmt);
6601  break;
6602  case 'x':
6603  if (command)
6604  {
6605  if (modified != CharT{'O'})
6606  {
6607 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
6608  ios::iostate err = ios::goodbit;
6609  f.get(is, nullptr, is, err, &tm, command, fmt+1);
6610  if ((err & ios::failbit) == 0)
6611  {
6612  checked_set(Y, tm.tm_year + 1900, not_a_year, is);
6613  checked_set(m, tm.tm_mon + 1, not_a_month, is);
6614  checked_set(d, tm.tm_mday, not_a_day, is);
6615  }
6616  is.setstate(err);
6617 #else
6618  // "%m/%d/%y"
6619  int ty = not_a_2digit_year;
6620  int tm = not_a_month;
6621  int td = not_a_day;
6622  read(is, ru{tm, 1, 2}, CharT{'/'}, ru{td, 1, 2}, CharT{'/'},
6623  rs{ty, 1, 2});
6624  checked_set(y, ty, not_a_2digit_year, is);
6625  checked_set(m, tm, not_a_month, is);
6626  checked_set(d, td, not_a_day, is);
6627 #endif
6628  }
6629  else
6630  read(is, CharT{'%'}, width, modified, *fmt);
6631  command = nullptr;
6632  width = -1;
6633  modified = CharT{};
6634  }
6635  else
6636  read(is, *fmt);
6637  break;
6638  case 'X':
6639  if (command)
6640  {
6641  if (modified != CharT{'O'})
6642  {
6643 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
6644  ios::iostate err = ios::goodbit;
6645  f.get(is, nullptr, is, err, &tm, command, fmt+1);
6646  if ((err & ios::failbit) == 0)
6647  {
6648  checked_set(H, tm.tm_hour, not_a_hour, is);
6649  checked_set(M, tm.tm_min, not_a_minute, is);
6650  checked_set(s, duration_cast<Duration>(seconds{tm.tm_sec}),
6651  not_a_second, is);
6652  }
6653  is.setstate(err);
6654 #else
6655  // "%T"
6656  using dfs = detail::decimal_format_seconds<Duration>;
6657  CONSTDATA auto w = Duration::period::den == 1 ? 2 : 3 + dfs::width;
6658  int tH = not_a_hour;
6659  int tM = not_a_minute;
6660  long double S;
6661  read(is, ru{tH, 1, 2}, CharT{':'}, ru{tM, 1, 2},
6662  CharT{':'}, rld{S, 1, w});
6663  checked_set(H, tH, not_a_hour, is);
6664  checked_set(M, tM, not_a_minute, is);
6665  checked_set(s, round_i<Duration>(duration<long double>{S}),
6666  not_a_second, is);
6667 #endif
6668  }
6669  else
6670  read(is, CharT{'%'}, width, modified, *fmt);
6671  command = nullptr;
6672  width = -1;
6673  modified = CharT{};
6674  }
6675  else
6676  read(is, *fmt);
6677  break;
6678  case 'C':
6679  if (command)
6680  {
6681  int tC = not_a_century;
6682 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
6683  if (modified == CharT{})
6684  {
6685 #endif
6686  read(is, rs{tC, 1, width == -1 ? 2u : static_cast<unsigned>(width)});
6687 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
6688  }
6689  else
6690  {
6691  ios::iostate err = ios::goodbit;
6692  f.get(is, nullptr, is, err, &tm, command, fmt+1);
6693  if ((err & ios::failbit) == 0)
6694  {
6695  auto tY = tm.tm_year + 1900;
6696  tC = (tY >= 0 ? tY : tY-99) / 100;
6697  }
6698  is.setstate(err);
6699  }
6700 #endif
6701  checked_set(C, tC, not_a_century, is);
6702  command = nullptr;
6703  width = -1;
6704  modified = CharT{};
6705  }
6706  else
6707  read(is, *fmt);
6708  break;
6709  case 'D':
6710  if (command)
6711  {
6712  if (modified == CharT{})
6713  {
6714  int tn = not_a_month;
6715  int td = not_a_day;
6716  int ty = not_a_2digit_year;
6717  read(is, ru{tn, 1, 2}, CharT{'\0'}, CharT{'/'}, CharT{'\0'},
6718  ru{td, 1, 2}, CharT{'\0'}, CharT{'/'}, CharT{'\0'},
6719  rs{ty, 1, 2});
6720  checked_set(y, ty, not_a_2digit_year, is);
6721  checked_set(m, tn, not_a_month, is);
6722  checked_set(d, td, not_a_day, is);
6723  }
6724  else
6725  read(is, CharT{'%'}, width, modified, *fmt);
6726  command = nullptr;
6727  width = -1;
6728  modified = CharT{};
6729  }
6730  else
6731  read(is, *fmt);
6732  break;
6733  case 'F':
6734  if (command)
6735  {

6742  CharT{'-'}, ru{tn, 1, 2}, CharT{'-'}, ru{td, 1, 2});

6756  case 'd':
6757  case 'e':

6759  {
6760 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE

6762 #else
6763  if (modified != CharT{'E'})
6764 #endif
6765  {
6766  int td = not_a_day;
6767  read(is, rs{td, 1, width == -1 ? 2u : static_cast<unsigned>(width)});
6768  checked_set(d, td, not_a_day, is);
6769  }
6770 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
6771  else if (modified == CharT{'O'})
6772  {
6773  ios::iostate err = ios::goodbit;
6774  f.get(is, nullptr, is, err, &tm, command, fmt+1);
6775  command = nullptr;

6778  if ((err & ios::failbit) == 0)
6779  checked_set(d, tm.tm_mday, not_a_day, is);
6780  is.setstate(err);
6781  }
6782 #endif
6783  else
6784  read(is, CharT{'%'}, width, modified, *fmt);
6785  command = nullptr;
6786  width = -1;
6787  modified = CharT{};
6788  }
6789  else
6790  read(is, *fmt);
6791  break;
6792  case 'H':
6793  if (command)
6794  {
6795 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
6796  if (modified == CharT{})
6797 #else
6798  if (modified != CharT{'E'})
6799 #endif
6800  {
6801  int tH = not_a_hour;
6802  read(is, ru{tH, 1, width == -1 ? 2u : static_cast<unsigned>(width)});
6803  checked_set(H, tH, not_a_hour, is);
6804  }
6805 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
6806  else if (modified == CharT{'O'})
6807  {
6808  ios::iostate err = ios::goodbit;
6809  f.get(is, nullptr, is, err, &tm, command, fmt+1);
6810  if ((err & ios::failbit) == 0)
6811  checked_set(H, tm.tm_hour, not_a_hour, is);
6812  is.setstate(err);
6813  }
6814 #endif
6815  else
6816  read(is, CharT{'%'}, width, modified, *fmt);
6817  command = nullptr;
6818  width = -1;
6819  modified = CharT{};
6820  }
6821  else
6822  read(is, *fmt);
6823  break;
6824  case 'I':

6826  {
6827  if (modified == CharT{})
6828  {

6830  // reads in an hour into I, but most be in [1, 12]
6831  read(is, rs{tI, 1, width == -1 ? 2u : static_cast<unsigned>(width)});
6832  if (!(1 <= tI && tI <= 12))
6833  is.setstate(ios::failbit);
6834  checked_set(I, tI, not_a_hour_12_value, is);
6835  }
6836  else
6837  read(is, CharT{'%'}, width, modified, *fmt);
6838  command = nullptr;

6840  modified = CharT{};
6841  }

6843  read(is, *fmt);

6848  if (modified == CharT{})

6852  checked_set(j, tj, not_a_doy, is);
6853  }

6923  }

6926  break;
6927  case 'n':
6928  case 't':
6929  if (command)
6930  {
6931  if (modified == CharT{})
6932  {
6933  // %n matches a single white space character
6934  // %t matches 0 or 1 white space characters
6935  auto ic = is.peek();
6936  if (Traits::eq_int_type(ic, Traits::eof()))
6937  {
6938  ios::iostate err = ios::eofbit;
6939  if (*fmt == 'n')
6940  err |= ios::failbit;
6941  is.setstate(err);
6942  break;
6943  }
6944  if (isspace(ic))
6945  {
6946  (void)is.get();
6947  }
6948  else if (*fmt == 'n')
6949  is.setstate(ios::failbit);
6950  }
6951  else
6952  read(is, CharT{'%'}, width, modified, *fmt);
6953  command = nullptr;
6954  width = -1;
6955  modified = CharT{};
6956  }
6957  else
6958  read(is, *fmt);
6959  break;
6960  case 'p':
6961  if (command)
6962  {
6963  if (modified == CharT{})
6964  {
6965  int tp = not_a_ampm;
6966 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
6967  tm = std::tm{};
6968  tm.tm_hour = 1;
6969  ios::iostate err = ios::goodbit;
6970  f.get(is, nullptr, is, err, &tm, command, fmt+1);
6971  is.setstate(err);
6972  if (tm.tm_hour == 1)
6973  tp = 0;
6974  else if (tm.tm_hour == 13)
6975  tp = 1;
6976  else
6977  is.setstate(err);
6978 #else
6979  auto nm = detail::ampm_names();
6980  auto i = detail::scan_keyword(is, nm.first, nm.second) - nm.first;
6981  tp = static_cast<decltype(tp)>(i);
6982 #endif
6983  checked_set(p, tp, not_a_ampm, is);
6984  }
6985  else
6986  read(is, CharT{'%'}, width, modified, *fmt);
6987  command = nullptr;
6988  width = -1;
6989  modified = CharT{};
6990  }
6991  else
6992  read(is, *fmt);
6993 
6994  break;
6995  case 'r':
6996  if (command)
6997  {
6998  if (modified == CharT{})
6999  {
7000 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
7001  ios::iostate err = ios::goodbit;
7002  f.get(is, nullptr, is, err, &tm, command, fmt+1);
7003  if ((err & ios::failbit) == 0)
7004  {
7005  checked_set(H, tm.tm_hour, not_a_hour, is);
7006  checked_set(M, tm.tm_min, not_a_hour, is);
7007  checked_set(s, duration_cast<Duration>(seconds{tm.tm_sec}),
7008  not_a_second, is);
7009  }
7010  is.setstate(err);
7011 #else
7012  // "%I:%M:%S %p"
7013  using dfs = detail::decimal_format_seconds<Duration>;
7014  CONSTDATA auto w = Duration::period::den == 1 ? 2 : 3 + dfs::width;
7015  long double S;
7016  int tI = not_a_hour_12_value;
7017  int tM = not_a_minute;
7018  read(is, ru{tI, 1, 2}, CharT{':'}, ru{tM, 1, 2},
7019  CharT{':'}, rld{S, 1, w});
7020  checked_set(I, tI, not_a_hour_12_value, is);
7021  checked_set(M, tM, not_a_minute, is);
7022  checked_set(s, round_i<Duration>(duration<long double>{S}),
7023  not_a_second, is);
7024  ws(is);
7025  auto nm = detail::ampm_names();
7026  auto i = detail::scan_keyword(is, nm.first, nm.second) - nm.first;
7027  checked_set(p, static_cast<int>(i), not_a_ampm, is);
7028 #endif
7029  }
7030  else
7031  read(is, CharT{'%'}, width, modified, *fmt);
7032  command = nullptr;
7033  width = -1;
7034  modified = CharT{};
7035  }
7036  else
7037  read(is, *fmt);
7038  break;
7039  case 'R':
7040  if (command)
7041  {
7042  if (modified == CharT{})
7043  {
7044  int tH = not_a_hour;
7045  int tM = not_a_minute;
7046  read(is, ru{tH, 1, 2}, CharT{'\0'}, CharT{':'}, CharT{'\0'},
7047  ru{tM, 1, 2}, CharT{'\0'});
7048  checked_set(H, tH, not_a_hour, is);
7049  checked_set(M, tM, not_a_minute, is);
7050  }
7051  else
7052  read(is, CharT{'%'}, width, modified, *fmt);
7053  command = nullptr;
7054  width = -1;
7055  modified = CharT{};
7056  }
7057  else
7058  read(is, *fmt);
7059  break;
7060  case 'S':
7061  if (command)
7062  {
7063  #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
7064  if (modified == CharT{})
7065 #else
7066  if (modified != CharT{'E'})
7067 #endif
7068  {
7069  using dfs = detail::decimal_format_seconds<Duration>;
7070  CONSTDATA auto w = Duration::period::den == 1 ? 2 : 3 + dfs::width;
7071  long double S;
7072  read(is, rld{S, 1, width == -1 ? w : static_cast<unsigned>(width)});
7073  checked_set(s, round_i<Duration>(duration<long double>{S}),
7074  not_a_second, is);
7075  }
7076 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
7077  else if (modified == CharT{'O'})
7078  {
7079  ios::iostate err = ios::goodbit;
7080  f.get(is, nullptr, is, err, &tm, command, fmt+1);
7081  if ((err & ios::failbit) == 0)
7082  checked_set(s, duration_cast<Duration>(seconds{tm.tm_sec}),
7083  not_a_second, is);
7084  is.setstate(err);
7085  }
7086 #endif
7087  else
7088  read(is, CharT{'%'}, width, modified, *fmt);
7089  command = nullptr;
7090  width = -1;
7091  modified = CharT{};
7092  }
7093  else
7094  read(is, *fmt);
7095  break;
7096  case 'T':
7097  if (command)
7098  {
7099  if (modified == CharT{})
7100  {
7101  using dfs = detail::decimal_format_seconds<Duration>;
7102  CONSTDATA auto w = Duration::period::den == 1 ? 2 : 3 + dfs::width;
7103  int tH = not_a_hour;
7104  int tM = not_a_minute;
7105  long double S;
7106  read(is, ru{tH, 1, 2}, CharT{':'}, ru{tM, 1, 2},
7107  CharT{':'}, rld{S, 1, w});
7108  checked_set(H, tH, not_a_hour, is);
7109  checked_set(M, tM, not_a_minute, is);
7110  checked_set(s, round_i<Duration>(duration<long double>{S}),
7111  not_a_second, is);
7112  }
7113  else
7114  read(is, CharT{'%'}, width, modified, *fmt);
7115  command = nullptr;
7116  width = -1;
7117  modified = CharT{};
7118  }
7119  else
7120  read(is, *fmt);
7121  break;
7122  case 'Y':
7123  if (command)
7124  {
7125 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
7126  if (modified == CharT{})
7127 #else
7128  if (modified != CharT{'O'})
7129 #endif
7130  {

7132  read(is, rs{tY, 1, width == -1 ? 4u : static_cast<unsigned>(width)});
7133  checked_set(Y, tY, not_a_year, is);
7134  }
7135 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE

7139  f.get(is, nullptr, is, err, &tm, command, fmt+1);
7140  if ((err & ios::failbit) == 0)
7141  checked_set(Y, tm.tm_year + 1900, not_a_year, is);
7142  is.setstate(err);
7143  }
7144 #endif
7145  else

7147  command = nullptr;

7150  }
7151  else
7152  read(is, *fmt);
7153  break;
7154  case 'y':
7155  if (command)
7156  {
7157 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
7158  if (modified == CharT{})
7159 #endif
7160  {
7161  int ty = not_a_2digit_year;
7162  read(is, ru{ty, 1, width == -1 ? 2u : static_cast<unsigned>(width)});
7163  checked_set(y, ty, not_a_2digit_year, is);
7164  }
7165 #if !ONLY_C_LOCALE
7166  else
7167  {
7168  ios::iostate err = ios::goodbit;
7169  f.get(is, nullptr, is, err, &tm, command, fmt+1);
7170  if ((err & ios::failbit) == 0)
7171  checked_set(Y, tm.tm_year + 1900, not_a_year, is);
7172  is.setstate(err);
7173  }
7174 #endif
7175  command = nullptr;
7176  width = -1;
7177  modified = CharT{};
7178  }
7179  else
7180  read(is, *fmt);
7181  break;
7182  case 'g':
7183  if (command)
7184  {
7185  if (modified == CharT{})
7186  {
7187  int tg = not_a_2digit_year;
7188  read(is, ru{tg, 1, width == -1 ? 2u : static_cast<unsigned>(width)});
7189  checked_set(g, tg, not_a_2digit_year, is);
7190  }
7191  else
7192  read(is, CharT{'%'}, width, modified, *fmt);

7194  width = -1;

7196  }
7197  else
7198  read(is, *fmt);
7199  break;
7200  case 'G':
7201  if (command)
7202  {
7203  if (modified == CharT{})
7204  {
7205  int tG = not_a_year;
7206  read(is, rs{tG, 1, width == -1 ? 4u : static_cast<unsigned>(width)});
7207  checked_set(G, tG, not_a_year, is);
7208  }
7209  else
7210  read(is, CharT{'%'}, width, modified, *fmt);
7211  command = nullptr;

7213  modified = CharT{};
7214  }
