7217  break;
7218  case 'U':
7219  if (command)
7220  {
7221  if (modified == CharT{})
7222  {
7223  int tU = not_a_week_num;
7224  read(is, ru{tU, 1, width == -1 ? 2u : static_cast<unsigned>(width)});
7225  checked_set(U, tU, not_a_week_num, is);
7226  }
7227  else
7228  read(is, CharT{'%'}, width, modified, *fmt);
7229  command = nullptr;
7230  width = -1;
7231  modified = CharT{};
7232  }
7233  else
7234  read(is, *fmt);
7235  break;
7236  case 'V':
7237  if (command)
7238  {
7239  if (modified == CharT{})
7240  {
7241  int tV = not_a_week_num;
7242  read(is, ru{tV, 1, width == -1 ? 2u : static_cast<unsigned>(width)});
7243  checked_set(V, tV, not_a_week_num, is);
7244  }
7245  else
7246  read(is, CharT{'%'}, width, modified, *fmt);
7247  command = nullptr;
7248  width = -1;
7249  modified = CharT{};
7250  }
7251  else
7252  read(is, *fmt);
7253  break;
7254  case 'W':
7255  if (command)
7256  {
7257  if (modified == CharT{})
7258  {
7259  int tW = not_a_week_num;
7260  read(is, ru{tW, 1, width == -1 ? 2u : static_cast<unsigned>(width)});
7261  checked_set(W, tW, not_a_week_num, is);
7262  }
7263  else
7264  read(is, CharT{'%'}, width, modified, *fmt);
7265  command = nullptr;
7266  width = -1;
7267  modified = CharT{};
7268  }
7269  else
7270  read(is, *fmt);
7271  break;
7272  case 'E':
7273  case 'O':
7274  if (command)
7275  {
7276  if (modified == CharT{})
7277  {
7278  modified = *fmt;
7279  }
7280  else
7281  {
7282  read(is, CharT{'%'}, width, modified, *fmt);
7283  command = nullptr;
7284  width = -1;
7285  modified = CharT{};
7286  }
7287  }
7288  else
7289  read(is, *fmt);
7290  break;
7291  case '%':
7292  if (command)
7293  {
7294  if (modified == CharT{})
7295  read(is, *fmt);
7296  else
7297  read(is, CharT{'%'}, width, modified, *fmt);
7298  command = nullptr;
7299  width = -1;
7300  modified = CharT{};
7301  }
7302  else
7303  command = fmt;
7304  break;
7305  case 'z':
7306  if (command)
7307  {
7308  int tH, tM;
7309  minutes toff = not_a_offset;
7310  bool neg = false;
7311  auto ic = is.peek();
7312  if (!Traits::eq_int_type(ic, Traits::eof()))
7313  {
7314  auto c = static_cast<char>(Traits::to_char_type(ic));
7315  if (c == '-')
7316  neg = true;
7317  }
7318  if (modified == CharT{})
7319  {
7320  read(is, rs{tH, 2, 2});
7321  if (!is.fail())
7322  toff = hours{std::abs(tH)};
7323  if (is.good())
7324  {
7325  ic = is.peek();
7326  if (!Traits::eq_int_type(ic, Traits::eof()))
7327  {
7328  auto c = static_cast<char>(Traits::to_char_type(ic));
7329  if ('0' <= c && c <= '9')
7330  {
7331  read(is, ru{tM, 2, 2});
7332  if (!is.fail())
7333  toff += minutes{tM};
7334  }
7335  }
7336  }
7337  }
7338  else
7339  {
7340  read(is, rs{tH, 1, 2});
7341  if (!is.fail())
7342  toff = hours{std::abs(tH)};
7343  if (is.good())
7344  {
7345  ic = is.peek();
7346  if (!Traits::eq_int_type(ic, Traits::eof()))
7347  {
7348  auto c = static_cast<char>(Traits::to_char_type(ic));
7349  if (c == ':')
7350  {
7351  (void)is.get();
7352  read(is, ru{tM, 2, 2});
7353  if (!is.fail())
7354  toff += minutes{tM};
7355  }
7356  }
7357  }
7358  }
7359  if (neg)
7360  toff = -toff;
7361  checked_set(temp_offset, toff, not_a_offset, is);
7362  command = nullptr;
7363  width = -1;
7364  modified = CharT{};
7365  }
7366  else
7367  read(is, *fmt);
7368  break;
7369  case 'Z':
7370  if (command)
7371  {
7372  if (modified == CharT{})
7373  {
7374  std::basic_string<CharT, Traits, Alloc> buf;
7375  while (is.rdstate() == std::ios::goodbit)
7376  {
7377  auto i = is.rdbuf()->sgetc();
7378  if (Traits::eq_int_type(i, Traits::eof()))
7379  {
7380  is.setstate(ios::eofbit);
7381  break;
7382  }
7383  auto wc = Traits::to_char_type(i);
7384  auto c = static_cast<char>(wc);
7385  // is c a valid time zone name or abbreviation character?
7386  if (!(CharT{1} < wc && wc < CharT{127}) || !(isalnum(c) ||
7387  c == '_' || c == '/' || c == '-' || c == '+'))
7388  break;
7389  buf.push_back(c);
7390  is.rdbuf()->sbumpc();
7391  }
7392  if (buf.empty())
7393  is.setstate(ios::failbit);
7394  checked_set(temp_abbrev, buf, {}, is);
7395  }
7396  else
7397  read(is, CharT{'%'}, width, modified, *fmt);
7398  command = nullptr;
7399  width = -1;
7400  modified = CharT{};
7401  }
7402  else
7403  read(is, *fmt);
7404  break;
7405  default:
7406  if (command)
7407  {
7408  if (width == -1 && modified == CharT{} && '0' <= *fmt && *fmt <= '9')
7409  {
7410  width = static_cast<char>(*fmt) - '0';
7411  while ('0' <= fmt[1] && fmt[1] <= '9')
7412  width = 10*width + static_cast<char>(*++fmt) - '0';
7413  }
7414  else
7415  {
7416  if (modified == CharT{})
7417  read(is, CharT{'%'}, width, *fmt);
7418  else
7419  read(is, CharT{'%'}, width, modified, *fmt);
7420  command = nullptr;
7421  width = -1;
7422  modified = CharT{};
7423  }
7424  }
7425  else // !command
7426  {
7427  if (isspace(static_cast<unsigned char>(*fmt)))
7428  {
7429  // space matches 0 or more white space characters
7430  if (is.good())
7431  ws(is);
7432  }
7433  else
7434  read(is, *fmt);
7435  }
7436  break;
7437  }
7438  }
7439  // is.fail() || *fmt == CharT{}
7440  if (is.rdstate() == ios::goodbit && command)
7441  {
7442  if (modified == CharT{})
7443  read(is, CharT{'%'}, width);
7444  else
7445  read(is, CharT{'%'}, width, modified);
7446  }
7447  if (!is.fail())
7448  {
7449  if (y != not_a_2digit_year)
7450  {
7451  // Convert y and an optional C to Y
7452  if (!(0 <= y && y <= 99))
7453  goto broken;
7454  if (C == not_a_century)
7455  {
7456  if (Y == not_a_year)
7457  {
7458  if (y >= 69)
7459  C = 19;
7460  else
7461  C = 20;
7462  }
7463  else
7464  {
7465  C = (Y >= 0 ? Y : Y-100) / 100;
7466  }
7467  }
7468  int tY;
7469  if (C >= 0)
7470  tY = 100*C + y;
7471  else
7472  tY = 100*(C+1) - (y == 0 ? 100 : y);
7473  if (Y != not_a_year && Y != tY)
7474  goto broken;
7475  Y = tY;
7476  }
7477  if (g != not_a_2digit_year)
7478  {
7479  // Convert g and an optional C to G
7480  if (!(0 <= g && g <= 99))
7481  goto broken;
7482  if (C == not_a_century)
7483  {
7484  if (G == not_a_year)
7485  {
7486  if (g >= 69)
7487  C = 19;
7488  else
7489  C = 20;
7490  }
7491  else
7492  {
7493  C = (G >= 0 ? G : G-100) / 100;
7494  }
7495  }
7496  int tG;
7497  if (C >= 0)
7498  tG = 100*C + g;
7499  else
7500  tG = 100*(C+1) - (g == 0 ? 100 : g);
7501  if (G != not_a_year && G != tG)
7502  goto broken;
7503  G = tG;
7504  }
7505  if (Y < static_cast<int>(year::min()) || Y > static_cast<int>(year::max()))
7506  Y = not_a_year;
7507  bool computed = false;
7508  if (G != not_a_year && V != not_a_week_num && wd != not_a_weekday)
7509  {
7510  year_month_day ymd_trial = sys_days(year{G-1}/December/Thursday[last]) +
7511  (Monday-Thursday) + weeks{V-1} +
7512  (weekday{static_cast<unsigned>(wd)}-Monday);
7513  if (Y == not_a_year)
7514  Y = static_cast<int>(ymd_trial.year());
7515  else if (year{Y} != ymd_trial.year())
7516  goto broken;
7517  if (m == not_a_month)
7518  m = static_cast<int>(static_cast<unsigned>(ymd_trial.month()));
7519  else if (month(static_cast<unsigned>(m)) != ymd_trial.month())
7520  goto broken;
7521  if (d == not_a_day)
7522  d = static_cast<int>(static_cast<unsigned>(ymd_trial.day()));
7523  else if (day(static_cast<unsigned>(d)) != ymd_trial.day())
7524  goto broken;
7525  computed = true;
7526  }
7527  if (Y != not_a_year && U != not_a_week_num && wd != not_a_weekday)
7528  {
7529  year_month_day ymd_trial = sys_days(year{Y}/January/Sunday[1]) +
7530  weeks{U-1} +
7531  (weekday{static_cast<unsigned>(wd)} - Sunday);
7532  if (Y == not_a_year)
7533  Y = static_cast<int>(ymd_trial.year());
7534  else if (year{Y} != ymd_trial.year())
7535  goto broken;
7536  if (m == not_a_month)
7537  m = static_cast<int>(static_cast<unsigned>(ymd_trial.month()));
7538  else if (month(static_cast<unsigned>(m)) != ymd_trial.month())
7539  goto broken;
7540  if (d == not_a_day)
7541  d = static_cast<int>(static_cast<unsigned>(ymd_trial.day()));
7542  else if (day(static_cast<unsigned>(d)) != ymd_trial.day())
7543  goto broken;
7544  computed = true;
7545  }
7546  if (Y != not_a_year && W != not_a_week_num && wd != not_a_weekday)
7547  {
7548  year_month_day ymd_trial = sys_days(year{Y}/January/Monday[1]) +
7549  weeks{W-1} +
7550  (weekday{static_cast<unsigned>(wd)} - Monday);
7551  if (Y == not_a_year)
7552  Y = static_cast<int>(ymd_trial.year());
7553  else if (year{Y} != ymd_trial.year())
7554  goto broken;
7555  if (m == not_a_month)
7556  m = static_cast<int>(static_cast<unsigned>(ymd_trial.month()));
7557  else if (month(static_cast<unsigned>(m)) != ymd_trial.month())
7558  goto broken;
7559  if (d == not_a_day)
7560  d = static_cast<int>(static_cast<unsigned>(ymd_trial.day()));
7561  else if (day(static_cast<unsigned>(d)) != ymd_trial.day())
7562  goto broken;
7563  computed = true;
7564  }
7565  if (j != not_a_doy && Y != not_a_year)
7566  {
7567  auto ymd_trial = year_month_day{local_days(year{Y}/1/1) + days{j-1}};
7568  if (m == 0)
7569  m = static_cast<int>(static_cast<unsigned>(ymd_trial.month()));
7570  else if (month(static_cast<unsigned>(m)) != ymd_trial.month())
7571  goto broken;
7572  if (d == 0)
7573  d = static_cast<int>(static_cast<unsigned>(ymd_trial.day()));
7574  else if (day(static_cast<unsigned>(d)) != ymd_trial.day())
7575  goto broken;
7576  j = not_a_doy;
7577  }
7578  auto ymd = year{Y}/m/d;
7579  if (ymd.ok())
7580  {
7581  if (wd == not_a_weekday)
7582  wd = static_cast<int>((weekday(sys_days(ymd)) - Sunday).count());
7583  else if (wd != static_cast<int>((weekday(sys_days(ymd)) - Sunday).count()))
7584  goto broken;
7585  if (!computed)
7586  {
7587  if (G != not_a_year || V != not_a_week_num)
7588  {
7589  sys_days sd = ymd;
7590  auto G_trial = year_month_day{sd + days{3}}.year();
7591  auto start = sys_days((G_trial - years{1})/December/Thursday[last]) +
7592  (Monday - Thursday);
7593  if (sd < start)
7594  {
7595  --G_trial;
7596  if (V != not_a_week_num)
7597  start = sys_days((G_trial - years{1})/December/Thursday[last])
7598  + (Monday - Thursday);
7599  }
7600  if (G != not_a_year && G != static_cast<int>(G_trial))
7601  goto broken;
7602  if (V != not_a_week_num)
7603  {
7604  auto V_trial = duration_cast<weeks>(sd - start).count() + 1;
7605  if (V != V_trial)
7606  goto broken;
7607  }
7608  }
7609  if (U != not_a_week_num)
7610  {
7611  auto start = sys_days(Sunday[1]/January/ymd.year());
7612  auto U_trial = floor<weeks>(sys_days(ymd) - start).count() + 1;
7613  if (U != U_trial)
7614  goto broken;
7615  }
7616  if (W != not_a_week_num)
7617  {
7618  auto start = sys_days(Monday[1]/January/ymd.year());
7619  auto W_trial = floor<weeks>(sys_days(ymd) - start).count() + 1;
7620  if (W != W_trial)
7621  goto broken;
7622  }
7623  }
7624  }
7625  fds.ymd = ymd;
7626  if (I != not_a_hour_12_value)
7627  {
7628  if (!(1 <= I && I <= 12))
7629  goto broken;
7630  if (p != not_a_ampm)
7631  {
7632  // p is in [0, 1] == [AM, PM]
7633  // Store trial H in I
7634  if (I == 12)
7635  --p;
7636  I += p*12;
7637  // Either set H from I or make sure H and I are consistent
7638  if (H == not_a_hour)
7639  H = I;
7640  else if (I != H)
7641  goto broken;
7642  }
7643  else // p == not_a_ampm
7644  {
7645  // if H, make sure H and I could be consistent
7646  if (H != not_a_hour)
7647  {
7648  if (I == 12)
7649  {
7650  if (H != 0 && H != 12)
7651  goto broken;
7652  }
7653  else if (!(I == H || I == H+12))
7654  {
7655  goto broken;
7656  }
7657  }
7658  }
7659  }
7660  if (H != not_a_hour)
7661  {
7662  fds.has_tod = true;
7663  fds.tod = hh_mm_ss<Duration>{hours{H}};
7664  }
7665  if (M != not_a_minute)
7666  {
7667  fds.has_tod = true;
7668  fds.tod.m_ = minutes{M};
7669  }
7670  if (s != not_a_second)
7671  {
7672  fds.has_tod = true;
7673  fds.tod.s_ = detail::decimal_format_seconds<Duration>{s};
7674  }
7675  if (j != not_a_doy)
7676  {
7677  fds.has_tod = true;
7678  fds.tod.h_ += hours{days{j}};
7679  }
7680  if (wd != not_a_weekday)
7681  fds.wd = weekday{static_cast<unsigned>(wd)};
7682  if (abbrev != nullptr)
7683  *abbrev = std::move(temp_abbrev);
7684  if (offset != nullptr && temp_offset != not_a_offset)
7685  *offset = temp_offset;
7686  }
7687  return is;
7688  }
7689 broken:
7690  is.setstate(ios::failbit);
7691  return is;
7692 }

7696 from_stream(std::basic_istream<CharT, Traits>& is, const CharT* fmt, year& y,

7706  y = fds.ymd.year();

7806 template <class Duration, class CharT, class Traits, class Alloc = std::allocator<CharT>>
7807 std::basic_istream<CharT, Traits>&
7808 from_stream(std::basic_istream<CharT, Traits>& is, const CharT* fmt,
7809  sys_time<Duration>& tp, std::basic_string<CharT, Traits, Alloc>* abbrev = nullptr,
7810  std::chrono::minutes* offset = nullptr)
7811 {
7812  using CT = typename std::common_type<Duration, std::chrono::seconds>::type;
7813  using detail::round_i;
7814  std::chrono::minutes offset_local{};
7815  auto offptr = offset ? offset : &offset_local;
7816  fields<CT> fds{};
7817  fds.has_tod = true;
7818  from_stream(is, fmt, fds, abbrev, offptr);
7819  if (!fds.ymd.ok() || !fds.tod.in_conventional_range())
7820  is.setstate(std::ios::failbit);
7821  if (!is.fail())
7822  tp = round_i<Duration>(sys_days(fds.ymd) - *offptr + fds.tod.to_duration());
7823  return is;
7824 }
